openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Irtdz7YugiusdFooImBogOQG|fc_0593218ebc10f81b0169cefe0334388198a4fff091c801da0e","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_NESoqmzgTSSFCdQsghlLOgzH|fc_0593218ebc10f81b0169cefe03343c81988a00fd247d10b18d","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_gray_readiness.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_gray_readiness.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37520,"output":411,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775172973789,"responseId":"resp_0593218ebc10f81b0169cefdf6f724819894eea57c2fb882a9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"740c5227","parentId":"84f7709a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T23:38:43.702Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_W1nciQUuWGySnTAmPOBTGw1y|fc_0593218ebc10f81b0169cefe0334208198aa070f74b0c5c4cb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 双因子单纸盘保守档灰度验证报告\n\n**生成时间**：2026-04-02 23:59  \n**Profile**：conservative（保守档）  \n**日期**：20260402  \n**纸盘**：aggressive\n\n---\n\n## 结论（Recommendation）\n\n> **HOLD（暂缓提升）**\n\n### 原因\n\n| 检查项 | 结论 |\n|--------|------|\n| live shadow 指标 | ✅ 全面优于 baseline |\n| 回撤改善 | ✅ 1.38pp（23.31%→21.93%） |\n| 夏普提升 | ✅ +0.23（1.942→2.172） |\n| risk_off / halt_new_buy guardrail | ⚠️ **触发**（baseline=True → dual=False） |\n| 是否建议提升至 default | ❌ 需先完成 guardrail 人工复核 |\n\n---\n\n## 核心指标对照\n\n### Live System（Shadow 回测）\n\n| 指标 | Baseline | Dual Factor Conservative | Diff（pp） | 方向 |\n|------|----------|--------------------------|------------|------|\n| 年化收益 | 68.39% | 85.63% | +17.24 | ✅ |\n| 最大回撤 | 23.31% | 21.93% | -1.38 | ✅ |\n| 夏普比率 | 1.942 | 2.172 | +0.23 | ✅ |\n| 年化波动率 | 28.93% | 30.57% | +1.63 | 中性 |\n| 最终净值 | 282.44 | 811.61 | +529.17 | ✅ |\n\n### Runtime Risk State（纸盘门禁）\n\n| 字段 | Baseline | Dual Shadow | 变化 |\n|------|----------|-------------|------|\n| strategy_max_dd_pct | 22.49 | 21.93 | -0.56 ✅ |\n| strategy_sharpe | 2.17 | 2.172 | +0.002 ✅ |\n| risk_off | **true** | **false** | ⚠️ 变化 |\n| halt_new_buy | **true** | **false** | ⚠️ 变化 |\n\n> ⚠️ **Guardrail 触发**：risk_off / halt_new_buy 从 True→False，必须人工复核后才可以灰度\n\n---\n\n## Guardrail 触发分析\n\n### 触发原因\n\n当日（20260402）市场状态：\n- 4/4 指数下跌（盘中 halt 触发）\n- market_breadth = 0.167 < 0.28（risk_off 阈值）\n- index_ret = -1.82% < -1.50%（halt 阈值）\n\n**Baseline 判定**：risk_off=true，halt_new_buy=true → FULL_HALT\n\n**Dual Factor Conservative Shadow**：\n- strategy_max_dd_pct = 21.93（改善了 0.56pp）\n- dual_multiplier = 0.855（压缩 gross，弱空头 regime）\n- 输出了 risk_off=false / halt_new_buy=false\n\n### 根本原因\n\ndual factor overlay 修改了 combo_v1 层面的 gross exposure（通过 dual_multiplier 压缩规模），导致同样 market breadth / index_ret 条件下，strategy_max_dd_pct 从 22.49 降至 21.93，理论上满足 halt 触发的边界条件。\n\n但 **shadow 的 runtime inputs 仅含 strategy 层面指标，不含 market-level halt 判断逻辑**。灰度接入后，主链路的 halt 逻辑（基于 market breadth / index_ret）保持独立，不受 dual factor 影响。\n\n**结论**：shadow 显示 halt_new_buy=false 属于预期行为（strategy 改善导致），live halt 逻辑与 dual factor 独立运行。但按 guardrail 规则必须人工确认。\n\n---\n\n## Profile 对照（Default vs Conservative）\n\n| 指标 | Conservative | Default | 备注 |\n|------|-------------|---------|------|\n| 年化收益 | 85.63% | 98.53% | default 更高但波动更大 |\n| 最大回撤 | 21.93% | 20.70% | default 更低 |\n| 夏普比率 | 2.172 | 2.323 | default 更优 |\n| dual_multiplier 最新 | 0.855 | 0.765 | conservative 更保守 |\n| 放大/收缩幅度 | ±5%~±10% | ±10%~±15% | — |\n\n---\n\n## 验证产物\n\n| 产物 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| Live Shadow Summary | `dual_factor_shadow_20260402_conservative_20260402_summary.json` |\n| Live Shadow Curve | `dual_factor_shadow_20260402_conservative_20260402_curve.csv` |\n| Live Shadow Payload | `dual_factor_shadow_20260402_conservative_20260402_live_payload.json` |\n| Paper Shadow Diff | `paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json` |\n| 本报告 | `dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json` |\n\n---\n\n## 下一步行动\n\n### Step 1（立即）：人工复核 guardrail\n- 确认 dual factor conservative 在同等 market state（breadth=0.167，index_ret=-1.82%）下 halt=false 是否为预期行为\n- 复核 dual factor 对 halt/risk_off 的影响机制（strategy 层 vs market 层）\n\n### Step 2（3~5 个交易日）：保守档连续 shadow 验证\n- 在不同 market state（非 halt 日）下运行保守档 shadow\n- 确认 dual factor 不导致异常 halt 误触发\n\n### Step 3（通过 Step 1+2 后）：确认 default 档灰度计划\n- Conservative 验证通过后，切换 dual_factor_profile=default\n- default 档同样需要完成 guardrail review\n\n---\n\n## 灰度 Readiness 总结\n\n| 验收标准 | 状态 |\n|----------|------|\n| conservative shadow 产物已生成 | ✅ PASS |\n| 核心指标（回撤/夏普/收益）均改善 | ✅ PASS |\n| 主链路 combo_v1 未被修改 | ✅ PASS |\n| risk_off/halt_new_buy guardrail 复核 | ⚠️ **待人工确认** |\n| 建议提升至 default 档 | ❌ HOLD |\n\n**总体结论**：conservative 档回测指标全面优秀，但因 guardrail 触发，**建议先完成人工复核，再决定是否进入 default 档或扩大灰度范围**。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775173123699}}
