{"type":"message","id":"6d3f4bdb","parentId":"cc1cf2ca","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:31:03.762Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_C1tsd9VDjni2Zg0W7sxoHoTr|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0a47525481988e3467b7c8639e8b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-03 07:18\nUpdated: 2026-04-03 07:49\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲要求继续推进 dual factor conservative 灰度结论后的下一步\nResume Entry: 先看 dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json、paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json，再检查 halt/risk_off 逻辑代码\n\n## Goal\n- 完成 dual factor conservative 档 guardrail 复核，并给出是否可继续进入 default 档或继续 conservative shadow 的可执行结论\n\n## Acceptance\n- 产出一份 guardrail 复核结果文件（md 或 json）\n- 明确回答 risk_off / halt_new_buy 从 True→False 是否属于预期\n- 给出下一步执行决策：继续 conservative 连续验证 / 进入 default / 保持 HOLD\n\n## Current\n- None\n\n## Next\n- None\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 23:58] 新建“单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证执行链”任务\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 生成单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证结果（JSON/MD）并完成 paper shadow diff 对照\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 得出 recommendation=HOLD：live shadow 改善，但 risk_off/halt_new_buy 从 True→False，需人工复核 guardrail 行为\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 提交单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证结果，commit=1dfc9ba50\n- 检查 risk_off / halt_new_buy 的主链路与 shadow 链路代码差异，确认 True→False 的根因是否为 inputs 粒度不同\n- 基于代码与 20260402 产物完成 conservative 档 guardrail 复核并生成报告\n- 得出执行结论：保持 HOLD，不进入 default；先统一 runtime truth 口径后继续 conservative shadow\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json\n- git commit 1dfc9ba50 feat(dual_factor): 双因子单纸盘conservative档灰度验证产出\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/