{"type":"message","id":"2128c8a0","parentId":"1382f159","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:31:20.406Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_OrA5HqfjzbJDCuB7xaZTwvoD|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0a56a0a08198b8a43b3b03543b07","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 32,\n      \"score\": 0.3941732615232467,\n      \"snippet\": \"## 00:16 低换手专项回测（2015-01~2026-03）\\n- 新增低换手专项脚本：`scripts/run_qlib_breadth_long_low_turnover_scan.py`。\\n- 修正换手口径：`run_qlib_breadth_robust_optimize_long.py` 改为基于 `order_indicator.trade_value` 统计。\\n- 扫描结果：grid=108，达成收益回撤约束 74 组，但 `turnover_ratio<=0.65` 为 0 组。\\n- 当前低换手优先候选：topk=12, n_drop=1, hold=5, risk=0.4，年化 48.94%，回撤 23.17%，夏普 2.641，turnover_ratio 62.7998。\\n\\n## 07:18 执行遗漏感知问题复盘（Durable）\\n- 用户指出“忘记执行任务”，根因是对“先对齐再执行”机械化处理，在“继续任务/看报告”场景先反问，造成延迟感知。\\n- 已修正流程：收到“继续任务/我要看报告/先给结果”时，优先直接汇报当前进度+报告路径，再进入下一步执行。\\n- 已落地文件：`AGENTS.md`、`USER.md`、`.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`。\\n\\n## 07:22 纸面实盘最终候选清单（Durable）\\n- 用户确认“好的”后，已直接产出最终候选与仓位建议（不再二次确认阻塞）。\\n- 新增报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper\\n\\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L1-L32\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/nightly_distill/2026-03-28.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 36,\n      \"score\": 0.39375050067901607,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 夜跑提炼 2026-03-28\\n\\n- started_at: 2026-03-28 23:02:50\\n- source_memory: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-28.md`\\n- source_learnings: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`\\n- source_nonempty_lines: 91\\n\\n## 高频主题\\n- 量化: 4\\n- 飞书: 2\\n- 面板: 0\\n- 模拟盘: 0\\n- 规则: 0\\n- 自动: 0\\n- 中文: 0\\n- 持仓: 5\\n- 报告: 1\\n- 夜跑: 0\\n\\n## 今日提炼\\n- 用户明确要求：当前飞书账号 `feishu-assistant` 应关联到 agent `xiaoguanjia`，而不是