{"type":"message","id":"38b1d5df","parentId":"dd830adb","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:31:30.408Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4MQ1VdVCbmVuQ5Jsj9x9oe4P|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0a61b5808198be9feaeca41db8bb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 最高层级任务连续执行清单（2026-03-19，2026-03-27 复核重开）\n\n> 规则：每完成一个最小验收件，立即进入下一个；除非出现阻断或用户改优先级，否则不得停在“已交付、未继续执行”的状态。\n\n## 当前最高层级任务\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## 执行队列\n\n### 已完成（历史落地）\n- [x] P0/P1 规则文件：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/quant_p0_p1_guard_rules_v1.json`\n- [x] P0 自动审计脚本：`scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py`\n- [x] tester 定时检验：`scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` + cron\n- [x] 模拟盘主链入口前阻断：`run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh`\n- [x] 账户结果 guard：`scripts/prewrite_paper_guard.py`\n- [x] 下午自动重跑强制刷新链完整自检：`scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py` + `scripts/cron_intraday_rebuild_paper_profiles_v1.sh` + `research/reports/intraday_recovery_automation_20260319.md`\n- [x] 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链（历史结论，需复核）：`scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate.py` + `scripts/check_stock_level_gate_chain.py` + `research/reports/stock_level_gate_chain_check_latest.md`\n- [x] 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版：`scripts/apply_paper_rollback.py` + `research/reports/paper_rollback_apply_20260319.md`\n- [x] 多源实时宽度兜底：`scripts/intraday_market_breadth.py` + `research/reports/intraday_breadth_fallback_progress_20260319.md`\n- [x] THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链\n  - stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py: DataFetcherManager (THS→Pytdx→Efinance→腾讯降级) ✅ 实测 002920 ¥113.75\n  - intraday_market_gate.py: 统一路由 + Tencent 降级 ✅ 实测 上证-1.39% 深证-2.02%\n  - intraday_market_breadth.py: 三源兜底 ✅ 实测 472涨/4499跌/9.5%\n  - commit: d499de8, 8743e3b, 083b938\n- [x] P0-006 真实接入复核：确认 v2 主链存在个股实时门禁调用，并修正静态审计误报\n  - 验收件：`research/reports/P0_006真实接入复核_20260327.md`\n  - 验收件：`research/reports/P0_006运行层产物缺失复核_20260327.md`\n  - 结果：`scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py` 最新 finding_count=5，`P0-006` 不再出现；`check_stock_level_gate_chain.py` 已补首个重跑窗口判断，11:34 前自检恢复 PASS\n\n### 重开（2026-03-27 根据最新审计）\n- [x] P0 新鲜度 guard：CSV 指数数据陈旧时，halt 判断必须显式降级或阻断\n  - 当前证据：`research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md` 报 `csv_index_data_stale`\n  - 最小验收件：规则或脚本补强 + tester/audit 可检测\n  - 验收件：`research/reports/P0_新鲜度_guard复核与补强_20260327.md`\n  - 结果：盘前“CSV 陈旧且无实时口径”已显式 halt；tester 不再对“已实时兜底”场景误报 `csv_index_data_stale`\n- [ ] P1-001 一致性收口：runtime / report / event_watch 的唯一真源与新鲜度门禁统一\n  - 当前证据：`research/reports/quant_p0_audit_latest.md` 与 `research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md`\n  - 最小验收件：一致性口径定义 + 至少一轮自动检验改善\n\n### 当前执行项\n- P1-001 一致性收口：runtime / report / event_watch 的唯一真源与新鲜度门禁统一\n\n## 强制执行规则\n1. 每轮只能选择一个 `[ ]` 项作为本轮最小验收件。\n2. 完成一个后，立即把下一个 `[ ]` 项升级为当前执行项，不得停留在空档。\n3. 若本轮无新增产物，汇报只能写：`无新增产物`。\n4. 若本轮修的是旁支，必须写：`旁支有新增，主任务无新增产物`。\n5. 若出现阻断，必须写清：阻断点 / 缺什么 / 为什么当前无法继续。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176290405}}
{"type":"message","id":"444f73cc","parentId":"38b1d5df","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:31:47.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Continuing Task Management**\n\nI need to keep working on the highest priority task since AGENTS says to sync the first unfinished queue item into Current. My ACTIVE_TASK seems outdated, so I might have to rebuild it to reflect the new task. I should probably check project files and related reports, especially within the quant project. The user mentioned I should execute and report evidence. Since ACTIVE_TASK exists but is done, I need to decide whether to rewrite the whole file or use CLI for an advance.\n\n**Reviewing Audit Reports**\n\nI need to read the latest audit reports and possibly the code. It seems like I should focus on producing a minimal deliverable, like a scope note or consistency plan, but I want to ensure it's actual progress rather than just a plan. Since the highest-priority acceptance mentions improvements, I might need to create a new report that captures the current consistency status and proposed changes, including any code adjustments. Let's inspect those reports to identify discrepancies.\n\n**Reading Audit and Tester Reports**\n\nI think it's time to check the latest audit and tester reports, along with any relevant scripts or documentation that refer to runtime, reporting, or event watching. This should help me gather the necessary information and get a better understanding of the current situation. I want to ensure I'm fully informed before proceeding, so digging into these resources seems like the right approach. Let's get started!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00990316fdaeab850169cf0a654e4c8198820fc8d099fb2e34\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzwpvyGZcYU_wYSWQHiAJQQpWQma4lQiuA1gdIDDyNnG-g1B4CYNmj-Sa3SuBijHHeuh368lidp2dcXl839P2TZlqzqnG7Qk7uODiYFjght5svOeEraEcm1S97y1kfnXxmU2Vp4Vo9Aw-smsn1W65aAAOk45CcEvqIx_8IlIYCPtoMchCsp1UMtO95BT4K05GE-KCVHap8u