{"type":"message","id":"9ad11ec7","parentId":"fa77b70c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:33:31.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing trading status**\n\nI need to look into the runtime state schema and generate a summary for the strategy probe guard. I'm noticing there's a potential issue with the state being \"risk_off\" while the trading status is \"TRADING.\" I wonder if this might be intentional, so I’ll need to understand that better. I'll read the relevant code sections and the p0_1 unified trading status acceptance for existing decisions. Searching the file may help clarify things, too.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00990316fdaeab850169cf0ad5f4388198a48877949362c4b1\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzwrbYN3J-Dm6GmDRwGlRZSoEskaUcn9gDs947KShwNwQ_HyNS-ZE35T97WfdTY8GmbIfWDZEjUKHV4Uwh3csT-kLimePq8bbHB1X4lpq0NKsDaVogn7CYX4a6jg4dHL4uJxdkt5A5tJMekdyx57iNt4ytxhjXC2Ww2S3bi5FmcfQc51BhPw_CbpZ2d3WRNmQjej9CfPyYf8VnIBnpdD1lyp_So7mARznG4xpZfC3D3IGLpx7IAxVlWWYoVVqviGQkQ5guXg699oXuv4lE4Npsiy5cyIc1qRcRN5DvyOv8u_nwOarTPcdaG2zhZ8AVvj0--UDQ5v-XV6_r8BxQyw21l8f_fXyF_xXvTUp4K5VmFnAUI-33W32jz1U1vIVrhvIafdgLA-khfHEyoYSk-WQiBXsMtk8mORGWm6kd_X1i8uMS_KiON_E3arNubttxPbPnyOcc19_KsmluTVWtYdpSYRyw_XN9jZEC_PAeNw732-dE3jiN2lNk08rXK2zmNVFILw5fquV9Opu4wz2S7byAW1ht9TvO613KqBzzd41GmcIN26e0PMg4Xk7WwFQB5sgfl86_X4AxKm4tWS6R-CZXUuAmM-aLo-3Lei4WkBxtGW65ZkAsTPnKRH4JguQUF42mNuOoK8vGjwjNrf4avgEJi8D5bI6pC07x3Ho1igIztI0GkLa42hu0Zz1ZLauBkRk7uKG_MAIZBMiM__E9KFXQDqfHfYyFd5f4yQcNyOeNufZhCbtU1cSPN-bHpar8-pq-UoWBNRVvTxdpvRYoEArOU_5mrDTlVVAdEm-7cHRoFOcauCMJkIi1X25ig_Fuo7Xh2Q_-AJ7VUiIExgAP9Xyp8j7V_LGbFQqH29LJxnOOlbUzS7xGdjV8ynJY2QdOMBRcwwlIeOBB1LhgDLJwTwRW_Jk6g3ksXSe8RcUhY7ul6faZWYLD3lSga8O7cTYo_kH7kQCz79kvCUrwCDuy6_rTor0EWh1OQ8c7w9sjuspeUlx8w38ZELw7zCRJ2Yx__5wBfKXR2ejfqYP70pFwi7RqHagdQgwXm4bscgBygeqHcFaqgRXwBziN0cymnlqBuIfuLsFzfLr1YGMiik73H3j5Nzy8aGLKQdvo5gQfZK3v4yPdFddIkVwkmFAnVbwe_ffycdPkg0J7CIKk2-42Hd9OWTTAwScT8hKB394rDONQPPLEruskQ0FDkdXg27ldQ949mMU0HnXfDX10NlCd_SP2CvmWoPpyM8XBFOduvp8OeGck0fkcqer47_4P_pL4YLRkT4c_09c_WREnwAChTioFAHe54AwS1qiBTOr9bDP5K-qKwEn5ZiUsC1PkvwyS69EkK4ZH2Fm4ziIazvzLqIZNlJiOCr3zKNStF2TpnEoDoi2W9E=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Analyzing trading status**\\n\\nI need to look into the runtime state schema and generate a summary for the strategy probe guard. I'm noticing there's a potential issue with the state being \\\"risk_off\\\" while the trading status is \\\"TRADING.\\\" I wonder if this might be intentional, so I’ll need to understand that better. I'll read the relevant code sections and the p0_1 unified trading status acceptance for existing decisions. Searching the file may help clarify things, too.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wvGUb0Awsi7HEe3c7N9LLspp|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62b48198b938bd4761daa652","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/runtime_state_schema.py","offset":180,"limit":140},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/runtime_state_schema.py\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":140}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3mmIJAX5hj9GTjqELcDClyTU|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62cc8198b4f62e4379bb67e1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_probe_guard.py","offset":130,"limit":210},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_probe_guard.py\",\"offset\":130,\"limit\":210}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_RON75biGkHerZO1p2FRDdasU|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62d08198b14886f6f36ae344","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_probe_guard_summary.py","offset":1,"limit":170},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_probe_guard_summary.py\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":170}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YsRP8BdlA5oxJgXhceAXn7SC|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62d88198948105268ffdafbe","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/p0_1_unified_trading_status_acceptance_20260325.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/p0_1_unified_trading_status_acceptance_20260325.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24431,"output":295,"cacheRead":147072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":171798,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775176400227,"responseId":"resp_00990316fdaeab850169cf0ad322f4819886b0c6aa39352ec8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"15ff7ac3","parentId":"9ad11ec7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:33:31.818Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_wvGUb0Awsi7HEe3c7N9LLspp|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62b48198b938bd4761daa652","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if force_state:\n        state = str(force_state).strip()\n    elif hard_stop or mode_text == \"halt\":\n        state = \"risk_halt\"\n    elif risk_off or halt_new_buy or mode_text == \"cautious\":\n        state = \"risk_off\"\n    elif pipeline_ok and precheck_passed is False:\n        state = \"blocked\"\n    elif pipeline_ok:\n        state = \"ok\"\n    else:\n        state = \"blocked\"\n\n    if not reason:\n        if state == \"risk_halt\":\n            reason = \"hard_stop_triggered\"\n        elif state == \"risk_off\":\n            reason = \"risk_gate_restricted_new_buy\"\n        elif state == \"blocked\" and precheck_passed is False:\n            reason = \"precheck_failed\"\n        elif state == \"blocked\" and (not pipeline_ok):\n            reason = \"pipeline_failed\"\n\n    advice_only = pipeline_ok and state in {\"risk_halt\", \"risk_off\", \"no_signal\"}\n    buy_authorized = pipeline_ok and state == \"ok\" and precheck_passed is not False\n    trading_ready = pipeline_ok and state == \"ok\"\n    severity = {\n        \"ok\": \"GREEN\",\n        \"no_signal\": \"YELLOW\",\n        \"risk_off\": \"YELLOW\",\n        \"risk_halt\": \"RED\",\n        \"blocked\": \"RED\",\n        \"no_data\": \"RED\",\n    }.get(state, \"RED\")\n    trading_status = derive_trading_status(\n        state=state,\n        mode=mode_text,\n        risk_off=bool(risk_off),\n        hard_stop=bool(hard_stop),\n        halt_new_buy=bool(halt_new_buy),\n        state_reason=reason,\n    )\n    gate_breakdown = classify_gate_reasons(reasons)\n    market_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"market\"]\n    style_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"style\"]\n    volatility_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"volatility\"]\n    liquidity_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"liquidity\"]\n    manual_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"manual\"]\n    other_reasons = gate_breakdown[\"other\"]\n    market_risk_state = derive_dimension_state(\"market\", market_reasons)\n    style_risk_state = derive_dimension_state(\"style\", style_reasons)\n    volatility_risk_state = derive_dimension_state(\"volatility\", volatility_reasons)\n    liquidity_risk_state = derive_dimension_state(\"liquidity\", liquidity_reasons)\n    primary_gate_dimension = \"none\"\n    if market_risk_state == \"halt\":\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"market\"\n    elif style_risk_state == \"halt\":\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"style\"\n    elif volatility_risk_state == \"halt\":\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"volatility\"\n    elif liquidity_risk_state == \"halt\":\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"liquidity\"\n    elif manual_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"manual\"\n    elif market_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"market\"\n    elif style_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"style\"\n    elif volatility_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"volatility\"\n    elif liquidity_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"liquidity\"\n    elif other_reasons:\n        primary_gate_dimension = \"other\"\n\n    return {\n        \"state\": state,\n        \"state_reason\": reason,\n        \"trading_status\": trading_status,\n        \"trading_status_reason\": reason,\n        \"trading_status_label_cn\": trading_status_to_cn(trading_status),\n        \"mode\": mode_text,\n        \"risk_off\": bool(risk_off),\n        \"hard_stop\": bool(hard_stop),\n        \"halt_new_buy\": bool(halt_new_buy),\n        \"gate_reasons\": reasons,\n        \"market_gate_reasons\": market_reasons,\n        \"style_gate_reasons\": style_reasons,\n        \"volatility_gate_reasons\": volatility_reasons,\n        \"liquidity_gate_reasons\": liquidity_reasons,\n        \"manual_gate_reasons\": manual_reasons,\n        \"other_gate_reasons\": other_reasons,\n        \"market_risk_state\": market_risk_state,\n        \"style_risk_state\": style_risk_state,\n        \"volatility_risk_state\": volatility_risk_state,\n        \"liquidity_risk_state\": liquidity_risk_state,\n        \"primary_gate_dimension\": primary_gate_dimension,\n        \"pipeline_ok\": bool(pipeline_ok),\n        \"precheck_passed\": precheck_passed,\n        \"advice_only\": advice_only,\n        \"buy_authorized\": buy_authorized,\n        \"trading_ready\": trading_ready,\n        \"severity\": severity,\n        \"source\": str(source or \"\"),\n    }\n\n\ndef build_precheck_runtime_truth(\n    *,\n    mode: str,\n    risk_off: bool,\n    hard_stop: bool,\n    halt_new_buy: bool,\n    halt_reason: str = \"\",\n    gate_reasons: list[str] | None = None,\n    precheck_passed: bool | None = None,\n    precheck_reasons: list[str] | None = None,\n    pipeline_ok: bool = True,\n    source: str = \"\",\n    empty_signal_reason: str = \"\",\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    reasons = _normalize_gate_reasons(precheck_reasons)\n    force_state = \"\"\n    force_reason = str(halt_reason or \"\").strip()\n    mode_text = str(mode or \"\").strip().lower()\n\n    if hard_stop and mode_text == \"halt\":\n        force_state = \"risk_halt\"\n        force_reason = force_reason or \"hard_stop_triggered\"\n    elif (risk_off or halt_new_buy) and mode_text in {\"cautious\", \"halt\"}:\n        force_state = \"risk_off\"\n        force_reason = force_reason or \"risk_gate_restricted_new_buy\"\n    elif reasons and all(reason in NO_SIGNAL_REASONS for reason in reasons):\n        force_state = \"no_signal\"\n        force_reason = str(empty_signal_reason or \"\").strip() or \"当日无可执行信号\"\n    elif not pipeline_ok:\n        force_state = \"blocked\"\n        force_reason = force_reason or \"precheck_process_failed\"\n    elif precheck_passed is False and reasons:\n        force_state = \"blocked\"\n\n[129 more lines in file. Use offset=320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176411816}}
{"type":"message","id":"86069112","parentId":"15ff7ac3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:33:31.820Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3mmIJAX5hj9GTjqELcDClyTU|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62cc8198b4f62e4379bb67e1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n    journal_df = read_csv(journal_path)\n    orders_df = read_csv(orders_path)\n    positions_df = read_csv(positions_path)\n    account_payload = load_json(account_path)\n    metrics_payload = load_json(metrics_path)\n    metrics = metrics_payload.get(\"metrics\", {}) or {}\n    # T05: Per-panel runtime risk truth — use panel-specific file if available\n    panel_risk_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"runtime_risk_state_latest_{profile_slug}.json\"\n    if panel_risk_path.exists():\n        runtime_state_path = panel_risk_path\n    else:\n        runtime_state_path = REPORT_DIR / \"runtime_risk_state_latest.json\"\n    runtime_payload = load_json(runtime_state_path)\n    runtime_truth = get_runtime_truth(runtime_payload)\n\n    runtime_truth_state = str(runtime_truth.get(\"state\") or \"\")\n    runtime_trading_status = str(runtime_truth.get(\"trading_status\") or \"\")\n    runtime_buy_authorized = bool(runtime_truth.get(\"buy_authorized\")) if runtime_truth else None\n    runtime_can_execute_today = bool(runtime_truth.get(\"trading_ready\")) if runtime_truth else None\n    runtime_blocking_reason = str(\n        runtime_truth.get(\"trading_status_reason\")\n        or runtime_truth.get(\"state_reason\")\n        or runtime_payload.get(\"halt_reason\")\n        or \"\"\n    )\n\n    issues: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n\n    drawdown_pct = parse_float(metrics.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\"), 0.0)\n    if drawdown_pct > parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_max_drawdown_pct\"), 8.0):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"RED\", \"code\": \"MAX_DRAWDOWN_BREACH\", \"value\": drawdown_pct, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_max_drawdown_pct\")})\n\n    daily_ret_raw = journal_df.get(\"pnl_day\")\n    if daily_ret_raw is None:\n        daily_ret = pd.Series([], dtype=float)\n    elif isinstance(daily_ret_raw, (int, float)):\n        daily_ret = pd.Series([daily_ret_raw])\n    else:\n        daily_ret = pd.to_numeric(daily_ret_raw, errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0)\n    nav = parse_float(account_payload.get(\"nav\"), 0.0)\n    if nav > 0 and len(daily_ret) > 0:\n        ret_series = daily_ret.tail(20) / nav\n    else:\n        ret_series = pd.Series(dtype=float)\n\n    trailing_20d_ret = trailing_return_pct(ret_series)\n    if trailing_20d_ret < parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_20d_return_floor_pct\"), -5.0):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"RED\", \"code\": \"RET_20D_BREACH\", \"value\": trailing_20d_ret, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_20d_return_floor_pct\")})\n\n    trailing_20d_sharpe = round(annualized_sharpe(ret_series.tail(20)), 3) if not ret_series.empty else 0.0\n    # 进取方案：early-stage grace（journal < 20天）跳过20d夏普检查\n    journal_records = int(len(journal_df))\n    early_stage = journal_records < int(cfg.get(\"admission\", {}).get(\"paper_observation_min_days\", 20))\n    if not early_stage and trailing_20d_sharpe < parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_20d_sharpe_floor\"), -0.5):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"YELLOW\", \"code\": \"SHARPE_20D_BREACH\", \"value\": trailing_20d_sharpe, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_20d_sharpe_floor\")})\n\n    avg_slippage = round(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"slippage\"), errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0).mean()), 2) if not journal_df.empty else 0.0\n    if avg_slippage > parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_avg_slippage_cap\"), 200.0):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"YELLOW\", \"code\": \"AVG_SLIPPAGE_BREACH\", \"value\": avg_slippage, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_avg_slippage_cap\")})\n\n    turnover_col = \"weight_after\"\n    avg_turnover = 0.0\n    if turnover_col in journal_df.columns and not journal_df.empty:\n        avg_turnover = round(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(turnover_col), errors=\"coerce\").diff().abs().fillna(0.0).mean()), 4)\n    if avg_turnover > parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_avg_turnover_cap\"), 0.12):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"YELLOW\", \"code\": \"AVG_TURNOVER_BREACH\", \"value\": avg_turnover, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_avg_turnover_cap\")})\n\n    journal_records = int(len(journal_df))\n    runtime_halt_blocked_orders = False\n    # 进取方案：journal grace days内只有INFO，不YELLOW；early_stage结束后才告警\n    journal_grace_days = int(parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_missing_journal_records_cap\"), 3.0))\n    if journal_records <= journal_grace_days and positions_df.empty:\n        # grace期内：INFO only，不阻塞\n        issues.append({\n            \"level\": \"INFO\",\n            \"code\": \"JOURNAL_GRACE_PERIOD\",\n            \"value\": journal_records,\n            \"limit\": journal_grace_days,\n            \"note\": \"paper启动初期或非交易时段，属正常\"\n        })\n        if not orders_df.empty:\n            runtime_halt_blocked_orders = (\n                bool(runtime_truth)\n                and runtime_buy_authorized is False\n                and runtime_trading_status in {\"BUY_HALT\", \"FULL_HALT\"}\n            )\n            if runtime_halt_blocked_orders:\n                issues.append(\n                    {\n                        \"level\": \"INFO\",\n                        \"code\": \"PLANNED_ORDERS_BLOCKED_BY_RUNTIME_HALT\",\n                        \"value\": int(len(orders_df)),\n                        \"limit\": 0,\n                    }\n                )\n    elif journal_records <= journal_grace_days and not positions_df.empty:\n        # grace期内但有持仓 → 正常运行，INFO\n        issues.append({\n            \"level\": \"INFO\",\n            \"code\": \"JOURNAL_GRACE_PERIOD_WITH_POSITIONS\",\n            \"value\": journal_records,\n            \"limit\": journal_grace_days,\n            \"note\": \"有持仓，journal未记载，属正常\"\n        })\n    elif not orders_df.empty and runtime_truth and runtime_truth.get(\"trading_status\") in {\"TRADING\", \"RISK_OFF\", \"CAUTIOUS\"}:\n        # 非grace期+正常交易日→正常no-activity\n        pass\n    elif journal_records > journal_grace_days and positions_df.empty:\n        # 超过grace期仍无持仓 → YELLOW\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"YELLOW\", \"code\": \"NO_ACTIVITY_DAY\", \"value\": journal_records, \"limit\": journal_grace_days})\n\n    error_trade_count = int(journal_df.get(\"risk_reason\", pd.Series(dtype=str)).astype(str).str.contains(\"error|reject|failed\", case=False, na=False).sum()) if not journal_df.empty else 0\n    if error_trade_count > int(parse_float(thresholds.get(\"paper_error_trade_count_cap\"), 0.0)):\n        issues.append({\"level\": \"RED\", \"code\": \"ERROR_TRADE_COUNT_BREACH\", \"value\": error_trade_count, \"limit\": thresholds.get(\"paper_error_trade_count_cap\")})\n\n    observation_days = int(cfg.get(\"admission\", {}).get(\"paper_observation_min_days\", 20))\n    status = \"GREEN\"\n    tomorrow_mode = \"normal\"\n    if any(item[\"level\"] == \"RED\" for item in issues):\n        status = \"RED\"\n        tomorrow_mode = \"halt\"\n    elif any(item[\"level\"] == \"YELLOW\" for item in issues):\n        status = \"YELLOW\"\n        tomorrow_mode = \"cautious\"\n    elif runtime_halt_blocked_orders:\n        status = \"GREEN\"\n        tomorrow_mode = \"observe\"\n    elif journal_records < observation_days:\n        # Journal 不足 observation_days 天数，但不构成告警；次日模式改为 observe\n        status = \"GREEN\"\n        tomorrow_mode = \"observe\"\n\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"config\": str(cfg_path),\n        \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n        \"profile_slug\": profile_slug,\n        \"status\": status,\n        \"tomorrow_mode\": tomorrow_mode,\n        \"issues\": issues,\n        \"runtime_truth\": {\n            \"source_path\": str(runtime_state_path),\n            \"state\": runtime_truth_state or None,\n            \"trading_status\": runtime_trading_status or None,\n            \"can_execute_today\": runtime_can_execute_today,\n            \"buy_authorized\": runtime_buy_authorized,\n            \"blocking_reason\": runtime_blocking_reason or None,\n        },\n        \"inputs\": {\n            \"journal\": str(journal_path),\n            \"orders\": str(orders_path),\n            \"account\": str(account_path),\n            \"metrics\": str(metrics_path),\n            \"positions\": str(positions_path),\n            \"runtime_risk_state\": str(runtime_state_path),\n        },\n        \"stats\": {\n            \"nav\": round(nav, 2),\n            \"planned_orders\": int(len(orders_df)),\n            \"journal_records\": journal_records,\n            \"position_count\": int(account_payload.get(\"position_count\", len(positions_df)) or 0),\n            \"max_drawdown_pct\": drawdown_pct,\n            \"trailing_20d_return_pct\": trailing_20d_ret,\n            \"trailing_20d_sharpe\": trailing_20d_sharpe,\n            \"avg_slippage\": avg_slippage,\n            \"avg_turnover_proxy\": avg_turnover,\n            \"error_trade_count\": error_trade_count,\n        },\n    }\n\n    out_json = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug + '_' if profile_slug else ''}probe_guard_{date_tag}.json\"\n    out_md = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug + '_' if profile_slug else ''}probe_guard_{date_tag}.md\"\n    out_latest = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug + '_' if profile_slug else ''}probe_guard_latest.json\"\n    out_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    out_latest.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    md_lines = [\n        f\"# 模拟盘/探针仓守卫结果（{date_tag}）\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- 状态: `{status}`\",\n        f\"- 次日模式: `{tomorrow_mode}`\",\n        f\"- 净值: `{payload['stats']['nav']}`\",\n        f\"- 日志记录数: `{journal_records}`\",\n        f\"- 最大回撤: `{drawdown_pct}%`\",\n        f\"- 近20日收益: `{trailing_20d_ret}%`\",\n        f\"- 近20日Sharpe: `{trailing_20d_sharpe}`\",\n        f\"- 平均滑点: `{avg_slippage}`\",\n        f\"- 平均换手代理: `{avg_turnover}`\",\n        f\"- 异常成交数: `{error_trade_count}`\",\n        f\"- 统一执行状态: `{runtime_truth_state or '-'}` / trading_status=`{runtime_trading_status or '-'}` / can_execute_today=`{runtime_can_execute_today}` / buy_authorized=`{runtime_buy_authorized}`\",\n        f\"- 统一阻断原因: `{runtime_blocking_reason or '-'}`\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## Issues\",\n    ]\n    if issues:\n        for item in issues:\n            md_lines.append(f\"- [{item['level']}] `{item['code']}` value=`{item['value']}` limit=`{item['limit']}`\")\n    else:\n        md_lines.append(\"- 无触发项\")\n    out_md.write_text(\"\\n\".join(md_lines) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    if args.push and status in {\"RED\", \"YELLOW\"}:\n        msg = \"\\n\".join(\n            [\n                f\"策略守卫告警｜{date_tag}｜{profile_slug or 'default'}\",\n                f\"状态: {status}\",\n                f\"次日模式: {tomorrow_mode}\",\n                f\"最大回撤: {drawdown_pct}%\",\n                f\"近20日收益: {trailing_20d_ret}%\",\n\n[17 more lines in file. Use offset=340 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176411818}}
{"type":"message","id":"43dbd878","parentId":"86069112","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:33:31.823Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_RON75biGkHerZO1p2FRDdasU|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62d08198b14886f6f36ae344","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nimport re\nimport shutil\nimport subprocess\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nDEFAULT_CONFIGS = [\n    PROJECT_ROOT / \"config\" / \"strategy_probe_guard_defensive_v1.json\",\n    PROJECT_ROOT / \"config\" / \"strategy_probe_guard_balanced_v1.json\",\n    PROJECT_ROOT / \"config\" / \"strategy_probe_guard_aggressive_v1.json\",\n]\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\")) if path.exists() else {}\n\n\ndef latest_date_tag() -> str:\n    files = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"paper_*_probe_guard_*.json\"))\n    if not files:\n        return datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    digits = re.findall(r\"(\\d{8})\", files[-1].name)\n    return digits[-1] if digits else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n\ndef push_feishu(message: str) -> tuple[bool, str]:\n    openclaw_bin = shutil.which(\"openclaw\")\n    if not openclaw_bin:\n        return False, \"openclaw_cli_missing\"\n    cmd = [\n        openclaw_bin,\n        \"message\",\n        \"send\",\n        \"--channel\",\n        \"feishu\",\n        \"--account\",\n        \"main\",\n        \"--target\",\n        \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n        \"-m\",\n        message,\n    ]\n    try:\n        proc = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=120)\n    except Exception as exc:\n        return False, f\"push_failed:{exc}\"\n    detail = ((proc.stdout or \"\").strip() or (proc.stderr or \"\").strip())[-2000:]\n    return proc.returncode == 0, detail\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"汇总三套 profile guard 状态\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date\", default=\"\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--push\", action=\"store_true\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    date_tag = args.date.strip() or latest_date_tag()\n    rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n\n    for cfg_path in DEFAULT_CONFIGS:\n        cfg = load_json(cfg_path)\n        profile_slug = str(cfg.get(\"profile_slug\") or \"\").strip()\n        # T05 fix: first try _latest.json (most recent result), fall back to dated file\n        dated_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug}_probe_guard_{date_tag}.json\"\n        latest_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug}_probe_guard_latest.json\"\n        report_path = latest_path if latest_path.exists() else (dated_path if dated_path.exists() else latest_path)\n        payload = load_json(report_path)\n        stats = payload.get(\"stats\", {}) or {}\n        issues = payload.get(\"issues\", []) or []\n        runtime_truth = payload.get(\"runtime_truth\", {}) or {}\n        rows.append(\n            {\n                \"profile_slug\": profile_slug,\n                \"profile_name\": cfg.get(\"profile_name\", profile_slug),\n                \"status\": payload.get(\"status\", \"NO_DATA\"),\n                \"tomorrow_mode\": payload.get(\"tomorrow_mode\", \"-\"),\n                \"runtime_truth_state\": runtime_truth.get(\"state\"),\n                \"trading_status\": runtime_truth.get(\"trading_status\"),\n                \"can_execute_today\": runtime_truth.get(\"can_execute_today\"),\n                \"buy_authorized\": runtime_truth.get(\"buy_authorized\"),\n                \"blocking_reason\": runtime_truth.get(\"blocking_reason\"),\n                \"planned_orders\": stats.get(\"planned_orders\", 0),\n                \"journal_records\": stats.get(\"journal_records\", 0),\n                \"position_count\": stats.get(\"position_count\", 0),\n                \"nav\": stats.get(\"nav\", 0.0),\n                \"max_drawdown_pct\": stats.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0),\n                \"trailing_20d_return_pct\": stats.get(\"trailing_20d_return_pct\", 0.0),\n                \"trailing_20d_sharpe\": stats.get(\"trailing_20d_sharpe\", 0.0),\n                \"avg_slippage\": stats.get(\"avg_slippage\", 0.0),\n                \"issue_count\": len(issues),\n                \"issue_codes\": \",\".join(str(item.get(\"code\", \"\")) for item in issues if item.get(\"code\")),\n                \"report_json\": str(report_path),\n            }\n        )\n\n    df = pd.DataFrame(rows)\n    status_rank = {\"RED\": 3, \"YELLOW\": 2, \"GREEN\": 1, \"NO_DATA\": 0}\n    df[\"status_rank\"] = df[\"status\"].map(status_rank).fillna(0).astype(int)\n    portfolio_status = df.sort_values([\"status_rank\", \"profile_slug\"], ascending=[False, True]).iloc[0][\"status\"] if not df.empty else \"NO_DATA\"\n    halt_count = int((df[\"tomorrow_mode\"] == \"halt\").sum()) if not df.empty else 0\n\n    out_csv = REPORT_DIR / f\"strategy_probe_guard_summary_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    out_json = REPORT_DIR / f\"strategy_probe_guard_summary_{date_tag}.json\"\n    out_md = REPORT_DIR / f\"strategy_probe_guard_summary_{date_tag}.md\"\n    latest_json = REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json\"\n    latest_md = REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.md\"\n\n    export_df = df.drop(columns=[\"status_rank\"]) if \"status_rank\" in df.columns else df\n    export_df.to_csv(out_csv, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8-sig\")\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n        \"portfolio_status\": portfolio_status,\n        \"halt_count\": halt_count,\n        \"rows\": export_df.to_dict(orient=\"records\"),\n        \"files\": {\"csv\": str(out_csv), \"md\": str(out_md)},\n    }\n    out_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    latest_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    md_lines = [\n        f\"# 三套 Profile Guard 总表（{date_tag}）\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- 总状态: `{portfolio_status}`\",\n        f\"- halt 数量: `{halt_count}` / `{len(df)}`\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 明细\",\n        export_df.to_markdown(index=False),\n        \"\",\n    ]\n    out_md.write_text(\"\\n\".join(md_lines) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    latest_md.write_text(\"\\n\".join(md_lines) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    if args.push:\n        lines = [\n            f\"三套 Guard 总表｜{date_tag}\",\n            f\"总状态: {portfolio_status}\",\n            f\"halt 数量: {halt_count}/{len(df)}\",\n        ]\n        for _, row in export_df.iterrows():\n            lines.append(\n                f\"- {row['profile_slug']}: {row['status']} / {row['tomorrow_mode']} / issues={row['issue_codes'] or 'none'}\"\n            )\n        lines.append(f\"报告: {out_md}\")\n        ok, detail = push_feishu(\"\\n\".join(lines))\n        payload[\"push\"] = {\"ok\": ok, \"detail\": detail}\n        out_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n        latest_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    print(json.dumps({\"status\": \"OK\", \"summary_csv\": str(out_csv), \"summary_md\": str(out_md), \"summary_json\": str(out_json)}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176411820}}
{"type":"message","id":"577fa427","parentId":"43dbd878","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:33:31.829Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YsRP8BdlA5oxJgXhceAXn7SC|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0adb62d88198948105268ffdafbe","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# P0-1 统一执行真相源验收报告（20260325）\n\n## 一、验收结论\n- 结论：`通过`\n- 本轮已把执行真相源统一到单一状态字段：`TRADING_ALLOWED / BUY_HALT / SELL_ONLY / FULL_HALT`\n- 控制塔主摘要已改为只展示 `统一交易状态`，不再要求人工同时解读 `risk_level + tomorrow_mode + runtime_truth_state`\n\n## 二、已落地改造\n- `scripts/runtime_state_schema.py`\n  - 新增统一状态枚举、中文标签、兼容旧 `runtime_truth` 的补齐逻辑\n  - 新增盘前预检专用构造函数，统一处理 `风险收缩 / 无信号 / review_required / 真故障`\n- `scripts/run_live_execution_v1.py`\n  - 盘前执行输出新增 `trading_status` / `trading_status_reason` / `runtime_truth`\n  - `live_precheck_v1_20260325.md` 已写入统一交易状态\n- `scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py`\n  - 对外状态改为统一状态枚举\n  - 优先复用执行引擎产出的 `runtime_truth`，不再自行拼旧状态词\n- `scripts/generate_control_tower_daily.py`\n  - 新增顶层 `trading_status`\n  - 控制塔摘要改为只展示一个统一交易状态字段\n\n## 三、当日验收证据\n- 盘中/运行态：\n  - `research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest.json`\n  - 最新 `runtime_truth.trading_status = BUY_HALT`\n  - 原因：`style_rotation_riskoff`\n- 收盘复盘：\n  - `research/reports/live_close_review_v2_20260325.json`\n  - 最新 `runtime_truth.trading_status = SELL_ONLY`\n  - 原因：`orders_pending_without_execution`\n  - 次日人工卖单交接单：`research/reports/live_nextday_manual_sell_handoff_20260325.json`\n- 控制塔：\n  - `research/reports/control_tower_daily_latest.json`\n  - 顶层 `trading_status.status = SELL_ONLY`\n  - `strategy_layer.trading_status = BUY_HALT`\n  - `execution_layer.trading_status = SELL_ONLY`\n- 盘前强检自动器：\n  - `research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260325.json`\n  - 最新 `status = BUY_HALT`\n  - `execution_truth.trading_status = BUY_HALT`\n\n## 四、回归结果\n- `pytest tests/test_runtime_state_schema.py tests/test_auto_run_premarket_precheck.py tests/test_run_live_execution_v1.py tests/test_live_close_review_chain.py`\n- 结果：`34 passed`\n\n## 五、边界说明\n- 这次完成的是 `P0-1`\n-