{"type":"message","id":"ce824b60","parentId":"5d875f94","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:34:38.988Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8p9vCbWPCFghExjno5ynuv3n|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b1e55b881989ff8e1ef73d534f9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if not path.exists():\n        return []\n\n    with path.open(\"r\", encoding=\"utf-8-sig\", newline=\"\") as f:\n        rows = list(csv.DictReader(f))\n    return rows[-limit:]\n\n\ndef load_csv_rows(path: Path) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return []\n    with path.open(\"r\", encoding=\"utf-8-sig\", newline=\"\") as f:\n        return list(csv.DictReader(f))\n\n\ndef file_state(path: Path, stale_hours: int = 24) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return {\"status\": \"RED\", \"path\": str(path), \"mtime\": \"\", \"reason\": \"missing\"}\n    mtime = datetime.fromtimestamp(path.stat().st_mtime)\n    age_hours = (datetime.now() - mtime).total_seconds() / 3600.0\n    status = \"GREEN\" if age_hours <= stale_hours else \"YELLOW\"\n    return {\n        \"status\": status,\n        \"path\": str(path),\n        \"mtime\": mtime.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"reason\": f\"age_hours={age_hours:.1f}\",\n    }\n\n\ndef _parse_dt_safe(text: Any) -> datetime | None:\n    value = str(text or \"\").strip()\n    if not value:\n        return None\n    for fmt in (\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\", \"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\", \"%Y-%m-%d\"):\n        try:\n            return datetime.strptime(value, fmt)\n        except Exception:\n            continue\n    return None\n\n\ndef _normalize_date_tag(value: Any) -> str:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    if len(text) == 8 and text.isdigit():\n        return text\n    if len(text) == 10 and text[4] == \"-\" and text[7] == \"-\":\n        compact = text.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if len(compact) == 8 and compact.isdigit():\n            return compact\n    return \"\"\n\n[1010 more lines in file. Use offset=110 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176478986}}
{"type":"message","id":"16c6cf5b","parentId":"ce824b60","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:34:38.990Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5MiSpVPclgxUorcF0mpbw67i|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b1e55d88198aed407c94ed2d252","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    }\n\n\ndef build_payload() -> dict[str, Any]:\n    expected_report_date_tag = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    expected_trade_date = resolve_expected_trade_date(expected_report_date_tag)\n    expected_trade_date_tag = expected_trade_date[\"date_tag\"]\n    incident_registry_mod.sync_registry(write=True)\n    today_report = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json\")\n    premarket_reviews = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"live_premarket_risk_v2_*.json\"))\n    premarket_review_path = premarket_reviews[-1] if premarket_reviews else None\n    premarket_review = load_json(premarket_review_path) if premarket_review_path else {}\n    guard_summary = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json\")\n    perf_panel = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_performance_panel_latest.json\")\n    breadth_alert_raw = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"breadth_strict_oos_alert_state.json\")\n    breadth_alert = normalize_breadth_alert_state(\n        breadth_alert_raw,\n        expected_trade_date_tag=expected_trade_date_tag,\n    )\n    runtime_state = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"runtime_risk_state_latest.json\")\n    future_leak_audit = load_json(REPORT_DIR / \"future_leak_walkforward_audit_latest.json\")\n    intervention_rows = load_csv_tail(REPORT_DIR / \"risk_intervention_log.csv\", limit=5)\n    profile_update_checks = [profile_update_state(profile_slug, expected_date_tag=expected_trade_date_tag) for profile_slug in TRACKED_ACCOUNT_PROFILES]\n    exact_live_review_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"live_close_review_v2_{expected_trade_date_tag}.json\"\n    latest_live_review_path = latest_report(\"live_close_review_v2_*.json\")\n    live_review_path = exact_live_review_path if exact_live_review_path.exists() else latest_live_review_path\n    live_review = load_json(live_review_path) if live_review_path else {}\n    execution_live_review_path = exact_live_review_path if exact_live_review_path.exists() else None\n    execution_live_review = load_json(execution_live_review_path) if execution_live_review_path else {}\n    exit_suite_reports = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"paper_exit_candidate_suite_*.json\"))\n    manual_review_summary = aggregate_manual_review_state()\n    governance_summary = governance_gate_state()\n\n    system_checks = {\n        \"strategy_report\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"premarket_runtime_v2\": file_state(premarket_review_path, stale_hours=72) if premarket_review_path else {\"status\": \"YELLOW\", \"path\": \"\", \"mtime\": \"\", \"reason\": \"missing\"},\n        \"strategy_governance_gate\": {\n            \"status\": governance_summary[\"status\"],\n            \"path\": governance_summary[\"path\"],\n            \"mtime\": governance_summary[\"mtime\"],\n            \"reason\": governance_summary[\"reason\"],\n        },\n        \"guard_summary\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"performance_panel\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_performance_panel_latest.html\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"breadth_aggressive\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"breadth_aggressive_paper_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"breadth_strict_oos\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"breadth_strict_oos_alert\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"breadth_strict_oos_alert_state.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"alpha55_account\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"paper_alpha55_account_v1_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"exit_dual_account\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"paper_exit_dual_account_v1_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"exit_tight_account\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"paper_exit_tight_account_v1_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"exit_candidate_suite\": file_state(exit_suite_reports[-1], stale_hours=72) if exit_suite_reports else {\"status\": \"RED\", \"path\": \"\", \"mtime\": \"\", \"reason\": \"missing\"},\n        \"future_leak_walkforward_audit\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"future_leak_walkforward_audit_latest.json\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"risk_intervention_log\": intervention_log_state(runtime_state),\n        \"manual_reconciliation\": {\n            \"status\": manual_review_summary[\"status\"],\n            \"path\": manual_review_summary[\"path\"],\n            \"mtime\": manual_review_summary[\"mtime\"],\n            \"reason\": manual_review_summary[\"reason\"],\n        },\n        \"manual_review_closure_alert\": manual_review_closure_alert_state(expected_report_date_tag),\n        \"incident_registry\": incident_registry_state(),\n        \"event_watch_refresh\": event_watch_refresh_state(expected_trade_date_tag),\n        \"live_chain_failures\": live_chain_failure_state(expected_trade_date_tag),\n        \"live_execution_integrity\": live_execution_integrity_state(\n            live_review,\n            live_review_path,\n            expected_date_tag=expected_trade_date_tag,\n        ),\n        \"comparison_dashboard\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"paper_profiles_comparison_latest.html\", stale_hours=72),\n        \"portal\": file_state(REPORT_DIR / \"dashboard_portal_latest.html\", stale_hours=72),\n\n[330 more lines in file. Use offset=790 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176478988}}
{"type":"message","id":"400195d8","parentId":"16c6cf5b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:34:38.994Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uVKS0GQ3dt4MUzUiEFu0RNzy|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b1e55e08198a1e2f1576432f017","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    elif \"YELLOW\" in statuses:\n        overall = \"YELLOW\"\n\n    strategy_layer = {\n        \"risk_mode\": today_report.get(\"risk_mode\", \"-\"),\n        \"risk_off\": bool(today_report.get(\"risk_off\", False)),\n        \"hard_stop\": bool(today_report.get(\"hard_stop\", False)),\n        \"runtime_truth_state\": str(get_runtime_truth(runtime_state).get(\"state\") or \"NO_DATA\"),\n        \"runtime_truth_ready\": bool(get_runtime_truth(runtime_state).get(\"trading_ready\")),\n        \"trading_status\": str(get_runtime_truth(runtime_state).get(\"trading_status\") or \"FULL_HALT\"),\n        \"trading_status_reason\": str(get_runtime_truth(runtime_state).get(\"trading_status_reason\") or \"\"),\n        \"manual_intervention_active\": any(\n            str(x) in {\"manual_hard_stop\", \"manual_risk_off\"}\n            for x in ((runtime_state.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}).get(\"gate_reasons\") or [])\n        ),\n        \"manual_intervention_reason\": str((runtime_state.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}).get(\"halt_reason\") or \"\"),\n        \"guard_portfolio_status\": guard_summary.get(\"portfolio_status\", \"NO_DATA\"),\n        \"guard_halt_count\": guard_summary.get(\"halt_count\", 0),\n        \"manual_review_complete\": bool(manual_review_summary.get(\"completed\")),\n        \"manual_review_pending_profiles\": manual_review_summary.get(\"pending_profiles\", []),\n        \"governance_status\": governance_summary.get(\"report_status\", \"UNKNOWN\"),\n        \"governance_generated_at\": governance_summary.get(\"generated_at\", \"\"),\n        \"governance_blocking_count\": len(governance_summary.get(\"blocking_issues\") or []),\n        \"governance_blocking_issues\": governance_summary.get(\"blocking_issues\", []),\n        \"report_date_tag\": expected_report_date_tag,\n        \"expected_trade_date_tag\": expected_trade_date_tag,\n        \"expected_trade_date_source\": expected_trade_date[\"source\"],\n        \"expected_date_tag\": expected_trade_date_tag,\n        \"profile_updates\": profile_update_checks,\n    }\n\n    execution_layer = build_execution_layer_snapshot(\n        execution_live_review,\n        execution_live_review_path,\n        expected_date_tag=expected_trade_date_tag,\n\n[285 more lines in file. Use offset=835 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176478990}}
{"type":"message","id":"54a0e082","parentId":"400195d8","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:35:57.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating JSON date checks**\n\nI’m considering adding a specialized function called `json_date_tag_state(path, expected_date_tag, stale_hours=72)` to verify the date_tag in JSON and possibly generated_at for guard_summary. There’s also a need to check event_watch and validate the expected date tag within the strategy_report file_state. I think the main improvement could come from the guard_summary check, but the report should include sources like event_watch and freshness from runtime_risk_state_latest. Generating an audit script and patching the guard_summary freshness seems ideal.\n\n**Creating an audit script**\n\nI think it might be necessary to build an audit script. It could feel a bit overwhelming, but I believe it’s manageable. Since the user wants to keep going and we need an actual artifact, I'll tackle both tasks: creating a new script called `scripts/check_p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency.py` and then running it. This way, I can ensure everything is consistent and aligned with what the user needs!\n\n**Patching the script**\n\nI’m considering how to patch `generate_control_tower_daily.py` by adding `json_date_tag_state` and possibly using `guard_summary` or even `strategy_report`. But actually, maybe that’s not necessary. I need to edit the file carefully with exact replacements. It’s crucial to read enough context around the imports — maybe there’s nothing needing to be imported? Yes, I think I can proceed with the patch. First, I’ll create the script to get started.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b271924819882c997652c49abb4\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzws5NmE_hL6osHc8ZYyChB1VlTmSjEYEFuWChZULiPOawJS8sIvVyqLNQnCMH709-D8tZGbm4IKJe1sp8J2D-6gguBfNMvOu2xIgy_AYdCkIJK1hVl3ptQ4S4_OOtXWiCXmZa_86wG-OkfmLx0CvwJ63ICc7swEgagaYa13aUG4E