9cyc9f5jxaDoSA9VH-KgUi33mD_YXpJTr_8ZkPuzvWFSRtVAU_PgfisxPsJ0r4I_it-M7U7IVxh-voGxvV56mdVXCNEqfAR9WYHr6slyO9lCkq7utLQYxJb7fQ8cmdSv3cpedqdhbkj2i2a2xFP2O13si8DcWiYXesIb9tWqlNmukYtccQj-n1kpBbHb4Vm5jy--yGsrX8GWIErEDvCpvUaYAmdejWHXc0O7c6Jm\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating JSON date checks**\\n\\nI’m considering adding a specialized function called `json_date_tag_state(path, expected_date_tag, stale_hours=72)` to verify the date_tag in JSON and possibly generated_at for guard_summary. There’s also a need to check event_watch and validate the expected date tag within the strategy_report file_state. I think the main improvement could come from the guard_summary check, but the report should include sources like event_watch and freshness from runtime_risk_state_latest. Generating an audit script and patching the guard_summary freshness seems ideal.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Creating an audit script**\\n\\nI think it might be necessary to build an audit script. It could feel a bit overwhelming, but I believe it’s manageable. Since the user wants to keep going and we need an actual artifact, I'll tackle both tasks: creating a new script called `scripts/check_p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency.py` and then running it. This way, I can ensure everything is consistent and aligned with what the user needs!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Patching the script**\\n\\nI’m considering how to patch `generate_control_tower_daily.py` by adding `json_date_tag_state` and possibly using `guard_summary` or even `strategy_report`. But actually, maybe that’s not necessary. I need to edit the file carefully with exact replacements. It’s crucial to read enough context around the imports — maybe there’s nothing needing to be imported? Yes, I think I can proceed with the patch. First, I’ll create the script to get started.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"开始落地审计脚本；产物会直接写到 research/reports，跑完就能给你验收件。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b39206481988efe9026c4f11b83\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_CBCipafZ86gDt7nbE0u2xQZw|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0b392de4819883e2804521aef643","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/check_p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nPROFILE_SLUGS = [\"defensive\", \"balanced\", \"aggressive\"]\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return {}\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef normalize_date_tag(value: Any) -> str:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    if len(text) == 8 and text.isdigit():\n        return text\n    if len(text) == 10 and text[4] == \"-\" and text[7] == \"-\":\n        compact = text.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if len(compact) == 8 and compact.isdigit():\n            return compact\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef issue(level: str, code: str, message: str, *, expected: Any = None, actual: Any = None, path: str = \"\") -> dict[str, Any]:\n    payload = {\n        \"level\": level,\n        \"code\": code,\n        \"message\": message,\n    }\n    if expected is not None:\n        payload[\"expected\"] = expected\n    if actual is not None:\n        payload[\"actual\"] = actual\n    if path:\n        payload[\"path\"] = path\n    return payload\n\n\ndef resolve_overall_status(issues: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> str:\n    levels = {item[\"level\"] for item in issues}\n    if \"RED\" in levels:\n        return \"RED\"\n    if \"YELLOW\" in levels:\n        return \"YELLOW\"\n    return \"GREEN\"\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    generated_at = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n\n    control_tower_path = REPORT_DIR / \"control_tower_daily_latest.json\"\n    guard_summary_path = REPORT_DIR / \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json\"\n    risk_intervention_path = REPORT_DIR / \"risk_intervention_audit_latest.json\"\n\n    control_tower = load_json(control_tower_path)\n    guard_summary = load_json(guard_summary_path)\n    risk_intervention = load_json(risk_intervention_path)\n\n    expected_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(\n        ((control_tower.get(\"strategy_layer\") or {}).get(\"expected_trade_date_tag\"))\n        or ((control_tower.get(\"strategy_layer\") or {}).get(\"expected_date_tag\"))\n        or guard_summary.get(\"date_tag\")\n        or risk_intervention.get(\"date_tag\")\n    )\n\n    issues: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    profile_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n\n    if not expected_date_tag:\n        issues.append(\n            issue(\n                \"RED\",\n                \"MISSING_EXPECTED_DATE_TAG\",\n                \"无法从 control_tower / guard_summary / risk_intervention 推导 expected_date_tag\",\n                path=str(control_tower_path),\n            )\n        )\n\n    runtime_paths = {\n        slug: REPORT_DIR / f\"runtime_risk_state_latest_{slug}.json\" for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS\n    }\n    probe_paths = {\n        slug: REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{slug}_probe_guard_latest.json\" for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS\n    }\n\n    runtime_payloads = {slug: load_json(path) for slug, path in runtime_paths.items()}\n    probe_payloads = {slug: load_json(path) for slug, path in probe_paths.items()}\n\n    guard_summary_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(guard_summary.get(\"date_tag\"))\n    if expected_date_tag and guard_summary_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\n        issues.append(\n            issue(\n                \"RED\",\n                \"STALE_GUARD_SUMMARY_DATE_TAG\",\n                \"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json 的 date_tag 落后于 expected_date_tag\",\n                expected=expected_date_tag,\n                actual=guard_summary_date_tag,\n                path=str(guard_summary_path),\n            )\n        )\n\n    risk_intervention_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(risk_intervention.get(\"date_tag\"))\n    if expected_date_tag and risk_intervention_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\n        issues.append(\n            issue(\n                \"YELLOW\",\n                \"RISK_INTERVENTION_DATE_TAG_MISMATCH\",\n                \"risk_intervention_audit_latest.json 未对齐 expected_date_tag\",\n                expected=expected_date_tag,\n                actual=risk_intervention_date_tag,\n                path=str(risk_intervention_path),\n            )\n        )\n\n    control_event_watch = (((control_tower.get(\"system_checks\") or {}).get(\"event_watch_refresh\")) or {})\n    if control_event_watch:\n        if str(control_event_watch.get(\"status\") or \"\") != \"GREEN\":\n            issues.append(\n                issue(\n                    \"RED\",\n                    \"CONTROL_TOWER_EVENT_WATCH_NOT_GREEN\",\n                    \"control_tower 的 event_watch_refresh 不是 GREEN\",\n                    actual=control_event_watch.get(\"status\"),\n                    path=str(control_tower_path),\n                )\n            )\n    else:\n        issues.append(\n            issue(\n                \"RED\",\n                \"MISSING_CONTROL_TOWER_EVENT_WATCH\",\n                \"control_tower 缺少 event_watch_refresh 检查项\",\n                path=str(control_tower_path),\n            )\n        )\n\n    for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS:\n        runtime_payload = runtime_payloads.get(slug) or {}\n        probe_payload = probe_payloads.get(slug) or {}\n        runtime_truth = runtime_payload.get(\"runtime_truth\") or {}\n        event_watch_refresh = runtime_payload.get(\"event_watch_refresh\") or {}\n\n        runtime_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(runtime_payload.get(\"date_tag\"))\n        probe_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(probe_payload.get(\"date_tag\"))\n        runtime_trading_status = str(runtime_truth.get(\"trading_status\") or \"\")\n        probe_trading_status = str(((probe_payload.get(\"runtime_truth\") or {}).get(\"trading_status\")) or \"\")\n        runtime_source = str(runtime_truth.get(\"source\") or \"\")\n\n        if expected_date_tag and runtime_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\n            issues.append(\n                issue(\n                    \"RED\",\n                    f\"RUNTIME_DATE_TAG_MISMATCH_{slug.upper()}\",\n                    f\"{slug} runtime_risk_state_latest 的 date_tag 未对齐 expected_date_tag\",\n                    expected=expected_date_tag,\n                    actual=runtime_date_tag,\n                    path=str(runtime_paths[slug]),\n                )\n            )\n\n        if expected_date_tag and probe_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\n            issues.append(\n                issue(\n                    \"RED\",\n                    f\"STALE_PROBE_GUARD_{slug.upper()}\",\n                    f\"{slug} paper_probe_guard_latest 的 date_tag 落后于 expected_date_tag\",\n                    expected=expected_date_tag,\n                    actual=probe_date_tag,\n                    path=str(probe_paths[slug]),\n                )\n            )\n\n        if probe_trading_status and runtime_trading_status and probe_trading_status != runtime_trading_status:\n            issues.append(\n                issue(\n                    \"RED\",\n                    f\"TRADING_STATUS_MISMATCH_{slug.upper()}\",\n                    f\"{slug} probe_guard.runtime_truth.trading_status 与 runtime_risk_state_latest 不一致\",\n                    expected=runtime_trading_status,\n                    actual=probe_trading_status,\n                    path=str(probe_paths[slug]),\n                )\n            )\n\n        if event_watch_refresh:\n            if not bool(event_watch_refresh.get(\"ok\")):\n                issues.append(\n                    issue(\n                        \"RED\",\n                        f\"EVENT_WATCH_FAILED_{slug.upper()}\",\n                        f\"{slug} runtime_risk_state_latest 的 event_watch_refresh 失败\",\n                        actual=event_watch_refresh,\n                        path=str(runtime_paths[slug]),\n                    )\n                )\n        else:\n            issues.append(\n                issue(\n                    \"RED\",\n                    f\"MISSING_EVENT_WATCH_REFRESH_{slug.upper()}\",\n                    f\"{slug} runtime_risk_state_latest 缺少 event_watch_refresh\",\n                    path=str(runtime_paths[slug]),\n                )\n            )\n\n        profile_rows.append(\n            {\n                \"profile_slug\": slug,\n                \"runtime_date_tag\": runtime_date_tag,\n                \"probe_date_tag\": probe_date_tag,\n                \"runtime_trading_status\": runtime_trading_status,\n                \"probe_trading_status\": probe_trading_status,\n                \"runtime_source\": runtime_source,\n                \"event_watch_ok\": bool(event_watch_refresh.get(\"ok\")) if event_watch_refresh else False,\n                \"event_watch_outputs\": event_watch_refresh.get(\"outputs\") if event_watch_refresh else [],\n            }\n        )\n\n    findings = {\n        \"trading_truth_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_<profile>.json -> runtime_truth.trading_status\",\n        \"report_layer_role\": \"paper_*_probe_guard_latest.json 与 strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json 为派生展示层，不得反向覆盖 runtime 真相\",\n        \"event_watch_role\": \"event_watch_refresh 是平台/信息新鲜度与健康检查输入，不直接作为 trading_status 真相字段；其异常应通过 runtime/control_tower 门禁上卷\",\n        \"freshness_gate\": \"所有展示层 date_tag 必须与 expected_date_tag 一致；不一致视为 stale\",\n    }\n\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": generated_at,\n        \"expected_date_tag\": expected_date_tag,\n        \"overall_status\": resolve_overall_status(issues),\n        \"findings\": findings,\n        \"issues\": issues,\n        \"profiles\": profile_rows,\n        \"inputs\": {\n            \"control_tower\": str(control_tower_path),\n            \"guard_summary\": str(guard_summary_path),\n            \"risk_intervention\": str(risk_intervention_path),\n            \"runtime_paths\": {k: str(v) for k, v in runtime_paths.items()},\n            \"probe_paths\": {k: str(v) for k, v in probe_paths.items()},\n        },\n    }\n\n    dated_json = REPORT_DIR / f\"p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_{expected_date_tag or 'unknown'}.json\"\n    latest_json = REPORT_DIR / \"p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_latest.json\"\n    dated_md = REPORT_DIR / f\"p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_{expected_date_tag or 'unknown'}.md\"\n    latest_md = REPORT_DIR / \"p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_latest.md\"\n\n    json_text = json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    dated_json.write_text(json_text, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    latest_json.write_text(json_text, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    md_lines = [\n        f\"# P1-001 runtime/report/event_watch 一致性审计（{expected_date_tag or 'unknown'}）\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- 生成时间：`{generated_at}`\",\n        f\"- 预期交易日：`{expected_date_tag or '-'}`\",\n        f\"- 总状态：`{payload['overall_status']}`\",\n        f\"- 交易真源：`{findings['trading_truth_source']}`\",\n        f\"- 报表角色：{findings['report_layer_role']}\",\n        f\"- event_watch 角色：{findings['event_watch_role']}\",\n        f\"- 新鲜度门禁：{findings['freshness_gate']}\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## Profiles\",\n        \"\",\n        \"| profile | runtime_date_tag | probe_date_tag | runtime_trading_status | probe_trading_status | event_watch_ok | source |\",\n        \"| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\",\n    ]\n    for row in profile_rows:\n        md_lines.append(\n            f\"| {row['profile_slug']} | {row['runtime_date_tag'] or '-'} | {row['probe_date_tag'] or '-'} | {row['runtime_trading_status'] or '-'} | {row['probe_trading_status'] or '-'} | {row['event_watch_ok']} | {row['runtime_source'] or '-'} |\"\n        )\n\n    md_lines.extend([\"\", \"## Issues\", \"\"])\n    if issues:\n        for item in issues:\n            md_lines.append(\n                f\"- [{item['level']}] `{item['code']}` {item['message']}（expected=`{item.get('expected', '-')}` actual=`{item.get('actual', '-')}` path=`{item.get('path', '-')}`）\"\n            )\n    else:\n        md_lines.append(\"- 无异常\")\n\n    md_text = \"\\n\".join(md_lines) + \"\\n\"\n    dated_md.write_text(md_text, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    latest_md.write_text(md_text, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    print(json.dumps({\n        \"status\": \"OK\",\n        \"overall_status\": payload[\"overall_status\"],\n        \"expected_date_tag\": expected_date_tag,\n        \"latest_json\": str(latest_json),\n        \"latest_md\": str(latest_md),\n    }, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/check_p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency.py\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport json\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Any\\n\\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \\\"research\\\" / \\\"reports\\\"\\nPROFILE_SLUGS = [\\\"defensive\\\", \\\"balanced\\\", \\\"aggressive\\\"]\\n\\n\\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    if not path.exists():\\n        return {}\\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\"))\\n\\n\\ndef normalize_date_tag(value: Any) -> str:\\n    text = str(value or \\\"\\\").strip()\\n    if len(text) == 8 and text.isdigit():\\n        return text\\n    if len(text) == 10 and text[4] == \\\"-\\\" and text[7] == \\\"-\\\":\\n        compact = text.replace(\\\"-\\\", \\\"\\\")\\n        if len(compact) == 8 and compact.isdigit():\\n            return compact\\n    return \\\"\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef issue(level: str, code: str, message: str, *, expected: Any = None, actual: Any = None, path: str = \\\"\\\") -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    payload = {\\n        \\\"level\\\": level,\\n        \\\"code\\\": code,\\n        \\\"message\\\": message,\\n    }\\n    if expected is not None:\\n        payload[\\\"expected\\\"] = expected\\n    if actual is not None:\\n        payload[\\\"actual\\\"] = actual\\n    if path:\\n        payload[\\\"path\\\"] = path\\n    return payload\\n\\n\\ndef resolve_overall_status(issues: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> str:\\n    levels = {item[\\\"level\\\"] for item in issues}\\n    if \\\"RED\\\" in levels:\\n        return \\\"RED\\\"\\n    if \\\"YELLOW\\\" in levels:\\n        return \\\"YELLOW\\\"\\n    return \\\"GREEN\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef main() -> None:\\n    generated_at = datetime.now().strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\\\")\\n\\n    control_tower_path = REPORT_DIR / \\\"control_tower_daily_latest.json\\\"\\n    guard_summary_path = REPORT_DIR / \\\"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json\\\"\\n    risk_intervention_path = REPORT_DIR / \\\"risk_intervention_audit_latest.json\\\"\\n\\n    control_tower = load_json(control_tower_path)\\n    guard_summary = load_json(guard_summary_path)\\n    risk_intervention = load_json(risk_intervention_path)\\n\\n    expected_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(\\n        ((control_tower.get(\\\"strategy_layer\\\") or {}).get(\\\"expected_trade_date_tag\\\"))\\n        or ((control_tower.get(\\\"strategy_layer\\\") or {}).get(\\\"expected_date_tag\\\"))\\n        or guard_summary.get(\\\"date_tag\\\")\\n        or risk_intervention.get(\\\"date_tag\\\")\\n    )\\n\\n    issues: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\\n    profile_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\\n\\n    if not expected_date_tag:\\n        issues.append(\\n            issue(\\n                \\\"RED\\\",\\n                \\\"MISSING_EXPECTED_DATE_TAG\\\",\\n                \\\"无法从 control_tower / guard_summary / risk_intervention 推导 expected_date_tag\\\",\\n                path=str(control_tower_path),\\n            )\\n        )\\n\\n    runtime_paths = {\\n        slug: REPORT_DIR / f\\\"runtime_risk_state_latest_{slug}.json\\\" for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS\\n    }\\n    probe_paths = {\\n        slug: REPORT_DIR / f\\\"paper_{slug}_probe_guard_latest.json\\\" for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS\\n    }\\n\\n    runtime_payloads = {slug: load_json(path) for slug, path in runtime_paths.items()}\\n    probe_payloads = {slug: load_json(path) for slug, path in probe_paths.items()}\\n\\n    guard_summary_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(guard_summary.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"))\\n    if expected_date_tag and guard_summary_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\\n        issues.append(\\n            issue(\\n                \\\"RED\\\",\\n                \\\"STALE_GUARD_SUMMARY_DATE_TAG\\\",\\n                \\\"strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json 的 date_tag 落后于 expected_date_tag\\\",\\n                expected=expected_date_tag,\\n                actual=guard_summary_date_tag,\\n                path=str(guard_summary_path),\\n            )\\n        )\\n\\n    risk_intervention_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(risk_intervention.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"))\\n    if expected_date_tag and risk_intervention_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\\n        issues.append(\\n            issue(\\n                \\\"YELLOW\\\",\\n                \\\"RISK_INTERVENTION_DATE_TAG_MISMATCH\\\",\\n                \\\"risk_intervention_audit_latest.json 未对齐 expected_date_tag\\\",\\n                expected=expected_date_tag,\\n                actual=risk_intervention_date_tag,\\n                path=str(risk_intervention_path),\\n            )\\n        )\\n\\n    control_event_watch = (((control_tower.get(\\\"system_checks\\\") or {}).get(\\\"event_watch_refresh\\\")) or {})\\n    if control_event_watch:\\n        if str(control_event_watch.get(\\\"status\\\") or \\\"\\\") != \\\"GREEN\\\":\\n            issues.append(\\n                issue(\\n                    \\\"RED\\\",\\n                    \\\"CONTROL_TOWER_EVENT_WATCH_NOT_GREEN\\\",\\n                    \\\"control_tower 的 event_watch_refresh 不是 GREEN\\\",\\n                    actual=control_event_watch.get(\\\"status\\\"),\\n                    path=str(control_tower_path),\\n                )\\n            )\\n    else:\\n        issues.append(\\n            issue(\\n                \\\"RED\\\",\\n                \\\"MISSING_CONTROL_TOWER_EVENT_WATCH\\\",\\n                \\\"control_tower 缺少 event_watch_refresh 检查项\\\",\\n                path=str(control_tower_path),\\n            )\\n        )\\n\\n    for slug in PROFILE_SLUGS:\\n        runtime_payload = runtime_payloads.get(slug) or {}\\n        probe_payload = probe_payloads.get(slug) or {}\\n        runtime_truth = runtime_payload.get(\\\"runtime_truth\\\") or {}\\n        event_watch_refresh = runtime_payload.get(\\\"event_watch_refresh\\\") or {}\\n\\n        runtime_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(runtime_payload.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"))\\n        probe_date_tag = normalize_date_tag(probe_payload.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"))\\n        runtime_trading_status = str(runtime_truth.get(\\\"trading_status\\\") or \\\"\\\")\\n        probe_trading_status = str(((probe_payload.get(\\\"runtime_truth\\\") or {}).get(\\\"trading_status\\\")) or \\\"\\\")\\n        runtime_source = str(runtime_truth.get(\\\"source\\\") or \\\"\\\")\\n\\n        if expected_date_tag and runtime_date_tag != expected_date_tag:\\n            issues.append(\\n                issue(\\n                    \\\"RED\\\",\\n                    f\\\"RUNTIME_DATE_TAG_MISMATCH_{slug.upper()}\\\",\\n                    f\\\"{slug} runtime_risk_state_latest 的 date_tag 未对齐 expected_date_tag\\\",\\n                    expected=expected_date_tag,\\n                    actual=runtime_date_tag,\\n                    path=str(runtime_paths[slug]),\\n                )\\n            )\\n\\n        if expected_date_tag a