rs/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_latest.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wwjaKYptzYno4yxH8XybGOF5|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e3a111c8198b76a5e57ff9a3451","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy_governance_gate_latest.json","offset":1,"limit":140},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy_governance_gate_latest.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":140}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tg7dL2S3nuV09BfbEaCfdcc4|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e3a113c8198997458d573befd17","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json","offset":1,"limit":140},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":140}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":87170,"output":229,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775177264752,"responseId":"resp_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e31eaa08198b51d31790d1e8599"}}
{"type":"message","id":"21cf049d","parentId":"51ea97c0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:47:55.243Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Tal2DQYjKtsFWbhCEFNNRN0P|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e3a1108819898a7f47983adfd70","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# dual factor conservative 档 guardrail 复核（2026-04-03）\n\n## 结论\n- **本轮结论：保持 HOLD，不进入 default 档。**\n- **可执行建议：继续 conservative shadow，但前提是先修正 / 统一 shadow 与 panel runtime truth 的门禁口径，再重跑 guardrail 验证。**\n- `risk_off / halt_new_buy` 在 `paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json` 中从 `True -> False`，**不应被视为“已通过 guardrail”**；这不是 2026-04-02 当日主链路真实风控结论放松，而是 **shadow / panel 运行时真相口径不一致** 造成的对照假象。\n\n## 直接判断\n### 1) True -> False 是否属于预期？\n- **对 shadow 输入层：属于可解释现象，但不是可放行结论。**\n  - `dual_factor_shadow_20260402_conservative_20260402_live_payload.json` 中 `runtime_shadow_inputs` 只带了：\n    - `strategy_max_dd_pct=21.93`\n    - `strategy_sharpe=2.172`\n    - `annual_return_pct=85.63`\n    - `annual_vol_pct=30.57`\n  - **没有携带 market-level gate 所需的 `index_ret_pct / market_breadth / intraday_gate / liquidity_state` 等信息**。\n  - 因此 shadow 层算出 `risk_off=false / halt_new_buy=false`，只能说明“仅按策略层指标看更宽松”，**不能代表主链路应该放开买入**。\n\n- **对主链路真实交易门禁：不属于应被接受的放松。**\n  - `runtime_risk_state_latest.json`（2026-04-02 15:34:22）明确是：\n    - `mode=halt`\n    - `risk_off=true`\n    - `hard_stop=true`\n    - `halt_new_buy=true`\n    - `trading_status=FULL_HALT`\n    - 原因包含：`index_ret_pct(-1.8200) <= -1.5000`、`market_breadth(0.1668) <= 0.2800`、`intraday_market_halt`\n  - `paper_aggressive_order_diagnostics_v1_20260402.json` 的实际执行产物也是：\n    - `mode=halt`\n    - `risk_off=true`\n    - `hard_stop=true`\n    - `halt_new_buy=true`\n    - `halt_reason=index_ret_pct(-1.9063) <= -1.5000`\n  - 说明 **2026-04-02 当天真实主链路并没有因为 conservative 双因子而放松门禁**。\n\n## 代码复核结论\n### A. 主链路风控代码本身没有支持“市场已 halt 但允许新买”\n1. `risk/risk_engine.py`\n   - `hard_stop=True` 时强制：`mode='halt'`、`risk_off=True`、`halt_new_buy=True`\n   - `risk_off=True` 时：`halt_new_buy = not allow_new_buy_when_riskoff`\n2. `scripts/regime_overlay_utils.py`\n   - 波动率 / 流动性进入 `risk_off` 时，会把 `halt_new_buy` 也拉成 `True`\n3. `scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py`\n   - 盘中 `gate_action='halt'` 时直接写入：`mode='halt'`、`risk_off=True`、`hard_stop=True`、`halt_new_buy=True`\n   - 盘中宽度极弱时同样会进入 halt\n\n**结论**：主链路设计上并不支持在 2026-04-02 这种 `4/4 指数下跌 + 宽度极弱` 的市场状态下，把 `halt_new_buy` 放开。\n\n### B. 真正的问题在 shadow / per-panel runtime truth 口径不一致\n1. `scripts/generate_per_panel_runtime_risk_t05.py`\n   - 该脚本生成 `runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json` 等 panel 文件时，核心只按：\n     - `paper_real_drawdown`\n     - `strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct`\n     - `strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct`\n   - 它会直接覆盖：\n     - 顶层 `runtime_truth`\n     - `latest_runtime`\n     - `base_runtime`\n   - **但没有把全局 market / intraday / liquidity gate 继承进来**。\n   - 实际证据：`runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json` 在同一时刻显示 `mode=normal, risk_off=false, halt_new_buy=false`，与全局 `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` 的 `FULL_HALT` 明显冲突。\n\n2. `scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py`\n   - 在 panel-level 分支里，会基于 panel drawdown threshold 对 `runtime_truth` 做 patch。\n   - live payload 的 `dual_factor_overlay.runtime_shadow_inputs` 又只保存策略层指标，不含 market-level truth。\n   - 这使得 shadow 对照很容易出现“策略层更优 -> False/False”，但主链路仍然应该 halt 的情况。\n\n## 关键证据\n### 证据 1：全局真实风控为 FULL_HALT\n- 文件：`research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest.json`\n- 关键值：\n  - `mode=halt`\n  - `risk_off=true`\n  - `halt_new_buy=true`\n  - `primary_gate_dimension=market`\n  - `trading_status=FULL_HALT`\n\n### 证据 2：per-panel 文件把同日状态改成了 normal\n- 文件：`research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json`\n- 关键值：\n  - `mode=normal`\n  - `risk_off=false`\n  - `halt_new_buy=false`\n  - `source=per_panel_t05_aggressive`\n- 判定：**panel generator 覆盖了全局市场门禁，导致 truth 漂移。**\n\n### 证据 3：实际 paper 执行产物仍然是 halt\n- 文件：`research/reports/paper_aggressive_order_diagnostics_v1_20260402.json`\n- 关键值：\n  - `mode=halt`\n  - `risk_off=true`\n  - `halt_new_buy=true`\n  - `halt_reason=index_ret_pct(-1.9063) <= -1.5000`\n- 判定：**真实执行链没有接受 shadow 中的 False/False 作为放行依据。**\n\n### 证据 4：conservative shadow diff 的 False/False 来自输入裁剪\n- 文件：`research/reports/paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json`\n- 关键值：\n  - baseline：`risk_off=true`、`halt_new_buy=true`\n  - dual shadow：`risk_off=false`、`halt_new_buy=false`\n- 同时文件自身也写明：`runtime_shadow_inputs` 仅含 strategy 指标，未携带 market-level halt/risk_off 信号。\n\n## 对 default 档的放行判断\n### 不放行的原因\n1. conservative 档 guardrail 还没有在**统一 runtime truth 口径**下通过。\n2. 当前已经发现：\n   - 全局 runtime truth\n   - per-panel runtime truth\n   - shadow runtime inputs\n   三套口径不一致。\n3. default 档 `dual_multiplier` 更激进（最新 0.765，较 conservative 的 0.855 更大幅偏离 1），如果在 truth 未统一前推进，只会放大验证噪音。\n\n## 建议执行路径\n### 当前建议\n- **决策：保持 HOLD，暂不进入 default。**\n- **执行动作：继续 conservative shadow，但先修一件事：统一 guardrail 对照口径。**\n\n### 建议的最小修复项\n1. `generate_per_panel_runtime_risk_t05.py`\n   - 生成 panel runtime truth 时，不要丢失全局 `market_gate_reasons / intraday_market_halt / liquidity_riskoff`。\n   - panel drawdown 只应覆盖“策略回撤维度”，不应覆盖市场维度的 halt 结论。\n2. `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py`\n   - shadow 对照输出里补齐 market-level runtime truth，至少把：\n     - `index_ret_pct`\n     - `market_breadth`\n     - `intraday_gate`\n     - `liquidity/volatility state`\n     一并写入 `runtime_shadow_inputs` 或单独写 `runtime_shadow_truth`。\n3. 修复后重跑：\n   - conservative 单纸盘 validation\n   - `paper_shadow_diff_conservative`\n   - 同日 paper order diagnostics 对照\n\n### 放行条件（进入 default 前必须满足）\n- 在统一口径后，conservative 档满足以下三条：\n  1. 同日 market halt 时，shadow 与主链路都保持 `halt_new_buy=true`\n  2. 非 halt 日里，dual factor 不产生异常的多余 blocked/halt\n  3. 连续 3~5 个交易日 shadow 结果稳定\n\n## 最终执行结论\n- **本次 guardrail 复核结果：未通过，不进入 default。**\n- **下一步：继续 conservative shadow，但必须先修正 runtime truth / shadow inputs 的门禁口径，再复跑验证。**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775177275236}}
{"type":"message","id":"2820f69a","parentId":"21cf049d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:47:55.250Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_suHsYxIJBIbK639GEaFv3GaX|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e3a111481988d98afd21cde0f36","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# P1-001 runtime/report/event_watch 一致性审计（20260402）\n\n- 生成时间：`2026-04-03 08:38:28`\n- 预期交易日：`20260402`\n- 总状态：`GREEN`\n- 交易真源：`runtime_risk_state_latest_<profile>.json -> runtime_truth.trading_status`\n- 报表角色：paper_*_probe_guard_latest.json 与 strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json 为派生展示层，不得反向覆盖 runtime 真相\n- event_watch 角色：event_watch_refresh 是平台/信息新鲜度与健康检查输入，不直接作为 trading_status 真相字段；其异常应通过 runtime/control_tower 门禁上卷\n- 新鲜度门禁：所有展示层 date_tag 必须与 expected_date_tag 一致；不一致视为 stale\n\n## Profiles\n\n| profile | runtime_date_tag | probe_date_tag | runtime_trading_status | probe_trading_status | event_watch_ok | source |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| defensive | 20260402 | 20260402 | TRADING | TRADING | True | per_panel_t05_defensive |\n| balanced | 20260402 | 20260402 | TRADING | TRADING | True | per_panel_t05_balanced |\n| aggressive | 20260402 | 20260402 | TRADING | TRADING | True | per_panel_t05_aggressive |\n\n## Issues\n\n- 无异常\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775177275243}}
