{"type":"message","id":"c6f75c9a","parentId":"87da5245","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:48:53.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，已经继续完，并给你落了一个**决策极简版**。\n\n本轮验收件\n- 新报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_conservative_decision_brief_20260403.md`\n- git 提交：`7dae98095`\n\n给决策用的极简结论\n- **现在不能进下一阶段**\n- **不能切 default**\n- **当前维持：HOLD**\n\n为什么\n1. **不是收益不行，恰恰是收益更好**\n- 年化：`68.39% -> 85.63%`\n- 最大回撤：`23.31% -> 21.93%`\n- 夏普：`1.942 -> 2.172`\n\n2. **之前 True -> False 不是放行信号**\n- 已确认那是 shadow / panel runtime truth 和主链路 market gate 口径不一致造成的假象\n- 这部分主干一致性我已经收口完成，`P1-001` 最新审计是 `GREEN`\n\n3. **现在剩下的是“真实阻断”，不是旧文件误判**\n- `strategy_governance_gate` 的 stale / 旧 dated 文件回退问题我已经修掉\n- 现在 control tower 里剩下的是**真实 BLOCK**\n\n当前真实风险点\n- 2026-04-02 当日主链路仍是 `FULL_HALT`\n- 当前还有 3 个真实 `drawdown_review_required`：\n  - `smallcap_chip_v4_1_alpha_guard`\n  - `smallcap_chip_v4_2_alpha_recover`\n  - `rd_agent_top2_gray_v1`\n\n下一步动作\n1. **不切 default，不扩大灰度**\n2. **继续 conservative shadow**\n3. **先补 3 个治理评审草案**\n4. **统一口径下再观察 3~5 个交易日**，稳定后再评估是否进 default\n\n一句话判断\n- **方向成立，但现在还不到放行时点。先做治理评审，再看连续 shadow。**\n\n如果你继续发“继续”，我下一步就直接给你落：\n**3 个 `drawdown_review_required` 的治理评审草案报告**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e6c0eb881988cda34e711f2b83d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":131,"output":502,"cacheRead":95488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775177322248,"responseId":"resp_00990316fdaeab850169cf0e6adedc8198bd485dd595a44805"}}
