{"type":"message","id":"e517caff","parentId":"83b464e7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:52:06.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，已继续并交付。\n\n本轮验收件\n- 报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy_drawdown_governance_review_draft_20260403.md`\n- 提交：`9d7a67f87`\n\n草案结论\n1. `smallcap_chip_v4_1_alpha_guard`\n- **建议：继续观察**\n- 理由：它本来就是稳健对照组/风控基线，有保留价值，但不适合作为主候选\n\n2. `smallcap_chip_v4_2_alpha_recover`\n- **建议：降级**\n- 理由：实验表现仍强，但已连续 `3/3` 触发 drawdown review，不适合继续维持“当前主候选”角色\n\n3. `rd_agent_top2_gray_v1`\n- **建议：下线候选**\n- 理由：它属于增强层，不是基础主链；当前又缺 `paper signoff + incident 约束`，同时连续触发评审，继续留在近期推进队列不划算\n\n当前执行口径\n- 在签字前，继续维持 `governance BLOCK`\n- 不恢复这 3 个策略的晋升/灰度放量动作\n\n如果你继续，我下一步可以直接做两件事里的一个：\n1. **把这份草案转成结构化 json 并接进 governance gate**\n2. **直接代你出一版“可签字正式版”**，把签字位、结论位、执行动作都整理好","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00990316fdaeab850169cf0f2ed5108198a1f2909a7a41117b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2448,"output":356,"cacheRead":113664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775177514787,"responseId":"resp_00990316fdaeab850169cf0f2dd0208198a4e0b65747e40fb6"}}
