{"type":"message","id":"1991cd42","parentId":"6b1fdcf7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:37:59.976Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_SnJSOkMRdh5OzVIvDDLUOcYl|fc_00990316fdaeab850169cf19f760ec819884f984a2b3bba055","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"lines.extend(\n        render_candidate_table(\n            \"## 六、今日优先候选池（基本面守门 v4.2b）\",\n            [\"排名\", \"代码\", \"名称\", \"综合分\", \"实时源\", \"实时价\", \"AI建议\", \"当前状态\", \"来源策略\"],\n            guard_table_rows,\n        )\n    )\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 七、今日模板信号摘要\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 可执行 BUY 候选数：`{executable_buy_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 研究层 BUY 候选数：`{raw_buy_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- SELL 候选数：`{sell_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 三盘合计决策可买入候选：`{decision_eligible_buy_total}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 三盘合计买入阻断数：`{blocked_buy_total}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 当前模式：`{risk_mode}`，市场宽度 `{fmt_ratio_pct(market_breadth, 2)}%`\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### BUY 候选（按模板顺序）\")\n    if display_tech_rows:\n        for row in display_tech_rows:\n            status_text = \"（仅观察，当前风控已阻断）\" if halt_new_buy else \"\"\n            lines.append(f\"- `{row.get('ts_code', '')}` {row.get('ai_stock_name', '')}{status_text}\".rstrip())\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- 暂无\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### SELL / 减仓关注（前15只）\")\n    if sell_rows[:15]:\n        for row in sell_rows[:15]:\n            lines.append(f\"- `{row.get('ts_code', '')}` {row.get('ai_stock_name', '')}\".rstrip())\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- 暂无\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 八、执行建议（当前时点）\")\n    if recommendation_status[\"blocked\"] and governance_status.get(\"blocking\"):\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：冻结新买入建议输出，先补治理材料、责任签字和决策记录。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 在治理恢复到 `PASS` 之前，候选池仅允许留在研究观察层，不允许作为执行优先级向下游透传。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 如果盘面随后修复，也不能绕过治理闸门直接恢复可执行买单。\")\n    elif halt_new_buy:\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：不追新仓，优先执行风险观察、持仓梳理与卖出条件复核。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若后续市场宽度修复，需要先复跑风控门控，再决定是否恢复开仓。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若继续维持弱宽度环境，则候选池仅保留为下一窗口的优先级参考，不转执行买单。\")\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：允许条件化推进，但必须先通过盘前强检、预算约束与用户确认。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若盘中风险灯号恶化，应立即退回观察态，不把候选池继续向执行层下钻。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若市场修复持续，可在用户确认后把优先候选整理成条件化试探单。\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 九、今日优先级结论\")\n    lines.append(\n        f\"1. **风险/治理状态**：`{risk_mode}`，市场宽度 `{fmt_ratio_pct(market_breadth, 2)}%`，\"\n        f\"执行建议 {'被阻断' if recommendation_status['blocked'] else '可条件化评估'}。\"\n    )\n    lines.append(f\"2. **候选优先级**：{'、'.join(f'`{code}`' for code in priority_codes) if priority_codes else '暂无'}。\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":43,"aggregated":"lines.extend(\n        render_candidate_table(\n            \"## 六、今日优先候选池（基本面守门 v4.2b）\",\n            [\"排名\", \"代码\", \"名称\", \"综合分\", \"实时源\", \"实时价\", \"AI建议\", \"当前状态\", \"来源策略\"],\n            guard_table_rows,\n        )\n    )\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 七、今日模板信号摘要\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 可执行 BUY 候选数：`{executable_buy_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 研究层 BUY 候选数：`{raw_buy_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- SELL 候选数：`{sell_count}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 三盘合计决策可买入候选：`{decision_eligible_buy_total}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 三盘合计买入阻断数：`{blocked_buy_total}`\")\n    lines.append(f\"- 当前模式：`{risk_mode}`，市场宽度 `{fmt_ratio_pct(market_breadth, 2)}%`\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### BUY 候选（按模板顺序）\")\n    if display_tech_rows:\n        for row in display_tech_rows:\n            status_text = \"（仅观察，当前风控已阻断）\" if halt_new_buy else \"\"\n            lines.append(f\"- `{row.get('ts_code', '')}` {row.get('ai_stock_name', '')}{status_text}\".rstrip())\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- 暂无\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### SELL / 减仓关注（前15只）\")\n    if sell_rows[:15]:\n        for row in sell_rows[:15]:\n            lines.append(f\"- `{row.get('ts_code', '')}` {row.get('ai_stock_name', '')}\".rstrip())\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- 暂无\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 八、执行建议（当前时点）\")\n    if recommendation_status[\"blocked\"] and governance_status.get(\"blocking\"):\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：冻结新买入建议输出，先补治理材料、责任签字和决策记录。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 在治理恢复到 `PASS` 之前，候选池仅允许留在研究观察层，不允许作为执行优先级向下游透传。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 如果盘面随后修复，也不能绕过治理闸门直接恢复可执行买单。\")\n    elif halt_new_buy:\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：不追新仓，优先执行风险观察、持仓梳理与卖出条件复核。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若后续市场宽度修复，需要先复跑风控门控，再决定是否恢复开仓。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若继续维持弱宽度环境，则候选池仅保留为下一窗口的优先级参考，不转执行买单。\")\n    else:\n        lines.append(\"- **主建议：允许条件化推进，但必须先通过盘前强检、预算约束与用户确认。**\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若盘中风险灯号恶化，应立即退回观察态，不把候选池继续向执行层下钻。\")\n        lines.append(\"- 若市场修复持续，可在用户确认后把优先候选整理成条件化试探单。\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 九、今日优先级结论\")\n    lines.append(\n        f\"1. **风险/治理状态**：`{risk_mode}`，市场宽度 `{fmt_ratio_pct(market_breadth, 2)}%`，\"\n        f\"执行建议 {'被阻断' if recommendation_status['blocked'] else '可条件化评估'}。\"\n    )\n    lines.append(f\"2. **候选优先级**：{'、'.join(f'`{code}`' for code in priority_codes) if priority_codes else '暂无'}。\")","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775180279967}}
{"type":"message","id":"d471f462","parentId":"1991cd42","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:38:39.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering governance recommendations**\n\nI’m thinking about adding lines if the governance status includes manual review recommendations. It might also be useful to mention the three suggested actions in cases where execution is blocked. That could be a nice touch! I’ll need to inspect the control tower's governance summary to see if that’s sufficient. After checking the registry rows, I can consider adding more details. Let's see how this all comes together!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00990316fdaeab850169cf1a1b2078819899f8fd4e88b50c2a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzxofEejgUiel8P-R2L74Favunkj-rr1rSqILLREGmLui1U5yh0NRvG8pWAJA4Z1vLIybOY69V-KKInbLsrMBEPGJRONTCYS2eVRamgGG6PRJBYVymgTPjtEUbj6lrihKPrP9kWTrJE8HRzGvVva7F0iw7k1jamavHSCNhf4spH6WiwkP0cwtjfp8rXe7LEYphHi2UFVB86NZ4p9EypBzEBJJ3QuRxNKy7rML5Wytki20icT7gARff3iP_9ZbaKWHbWjw5eyptjh9Z0YJEEvophf4hJnlc8Nps01c6lIyW5-1d9eikQ_nnqZXK5X4oJTkM1ugXcPP8dU2JSZwdNV9_J4vdNuLR3JCI6MuNFID5r-UGjnBLaDHbaS4E5ay4S5sFTEozXLA38edcHjMEc1hI_Oja25MNY84HWPH19xECf3ZeRgGImPSET3T__Bw_PnwNg95TL2-3Ci2EG3wMW5si1hUp4-rnacE4XNYv14eyYLU1RJsuO16nAqxWx3ZQylUX1qv3TS4INnYrzxp3CPuh3PzosqBaVt4dND0ub-HZx0rnyFXNEHV1uVsGqSjUzvJvJ4kBll3dQKSR-i9zVbyuzMQ5Ol6lNlNJje46BnxM14C2VocHtIBL-pvVvkAYARgMLSfs4go_zMtq6WSCpeJrS-6NtzsidZ4Otrwqo_Y7OMsv5jnXbjpuzPGx00x_yj2OXT0bWksoPOuvRzn4IlMWT5IWzMYDZqoQON8NYl4LiPoc-AQdRosp6KAKmo5_xcvDzfdvZQ8gtj31MpDuRha8gLtTVtHAmd-H5oLYO_IzDNfPC1OCs1avtadn7i6mfYkkkRS7PoyxiPKN8saS8JVqLoO5B49nPn717NynQi4GtsH1XFSI2p-h2uNDf8aE29VJzcySzQJhSJR-CcLRvIreICgIl0aQMgyqyvMTJGMVQrZROwiY_vNOKG42_NrMjkwV6W94NucFPSUAhIAWTsX56XGzPComHGy4kb9cL3GdaaUIpH4o0cXikFwtHE1ijLg8Tw2p6BPQkmW_-faLDRWx4MtSpW9Qmh7pQTrO1qmMBixyo502xHyTJvJ4mHpdOrYYj5nxKAZLm46ffjT12uEKiuh6liWEh6B1VXXziuJZPXHIOQKmbS6wdSjWhF0wijhxYohKw6KSNRXnpN2J-ReX3beMZ6QPXRYHvan8dZ53LOVM4oRSIR8izMQIOrK9Se11te6\