w to be signed off on. Since the governance review is already wired into the system, the immediate blocker is getting that formal sign-off from the user, which is a manual step I can't complete for them. I'm narrowing down to what I can actually do now without blocking on human input. The conservative shadow needs 3-5 days of continuous observation, but I can set up the monitoring framework today so everything's ready to go once those days pass. I'll update the task tracking and start preparing the shadow environment for the observation period.","thinkingSignature":"16a22cc0811f7db197593646c5a032455064a0b0a7940faf0d2c871b7561a2af"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，继续。上游建议层已接入，下一步按\"建议下一步\"执行：先跑 conservative shadow 的连续观察，同时保持 BLOCK。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tqk5v56tr3df_1","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","content":"Status: active\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-03 10:24\nUpdated: 2026-04-03 10:24\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲要求继续推进下一步\nResume Entry: 先在统一口径下跑一轮 conservative shadow 重跑（runtime truth 已统一），再明确下一步是连续 3~5 日观察还是补 governance 签字\n\n## Goal\n- 在 P1-001 一致性收口完成、runtime truth 口径统一后，跑一轮 conservative shadow 并更新结论\n\n## Acceptance\n- conservative shadow 已在统一后的 runtime truth 口径下重新运行\n- 产出最新 shadow 报告（20260403）\n- 明确下一步：连续观察 3~5 日 还是补 governance 签字\n\n## Current\n- 在统一口径下跑 conservative shadow 重跑\n\n## Next\n- 分析 shadow 结果，更新连续观察状态\n- 明确 BLOCK 是否解除或维持\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-03 08:52] 3 个 drawdown_review_required 治理评审草案落地\n- [2026-04-03 08:54] 结构化 JSON + 可签字正式版落地\n- [2026-04-03 10:18] 评审建议接入 governance gate 链路，提交 f9d931e6f\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/p1_runtime_report_event_watch_consistency_latest.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/strategy