{"type":"message","id":"24aaf626","parentId":"99c26b22","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:25:43.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give a clear, concise report to 张玲.","thinkingSignature":"d6a04ccf1fa34fa334a875ba2234906d09804cf2a9df6380eba3c4b2dfd5ee15"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已继续并交付。\n\n本轮验收件\n- conservative shadow 在统一 runtime truth 口径下重跑完成\n- 提交：`bf10859ec`\n- 产物：`live_system_v1_20260403.json`（conservative shadow 最新结果）\n\nconservative shadow 最新结果（统一口径后）\n- 年化收益：`85.63%`（baseline `68.39%`，差 `+17.24pp`）\n- 最大回撤：`21.93%`（baseline `23.31%`，差 `-1.38pp`）\n- 夏普：`2.172`（baseline `1.942`，差 `+0.23`）\n\n这证明之前的优势**不是因为口径问题**，是真实的方向性成立。\n\n当前局面\n- 方向：conservative shadow 持续优于 baseline ✓\n- 口径：runtime truth 已统一，conservative 不再受口径干扰 ✓\n- BLOCK：**未解除**，需要 governance review 签字\n- 市场：`FULL_HALT`，conservative 仍不宜推进\n\n下一步两条路，都需要你决定\n1. **补签字**：把 `strategy_drawdown_governance_review_signoff_20260403.md` 签完，解除 BLOCK\n2. **连续观察**：conservative shadow 继续跑 3~5 个交易日，再做灰度决策"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92419,"output":298,"cacheRead":25986,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118703,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775183131940,"responseId":"061e581caa024f10f399bc448594ce91"}}
