{"type":"message","id":"400ce8f5","parentId":"2a797cfe","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:34:44.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the config. The `coding-agent` has `model.primary = gmn/gpt-5.4`. The user wants to change it to `minimax-m2.7` (which maps to `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7`). \n\nI need to update `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`, changing the `coding-agent` entry's model from `gmn/gpt-5.4` to `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7`.\n\nLet me do this carefully with a Python script to avoid corrupting the JSON.","thinkingSignature":"4db18ab84d5245843daa41b0dadeb491eacdb0cc26ec22a35b67b2c8c1eb8869"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。`coding-agent` 当前配置是 `gmn/gpt-5.4`，改成 `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7`。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lsjxzrjuv7jt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nconfig_path = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"openclaw.json\"\nconfig = json.loads(config_path.read_text())\n\nagents = config.get(\"agents\", {}).get(\"list\", [])\nfor agent in agents:\n    if agent.get(\"id\") == \"coding-agent\":\n        old = agent.get(\"model\")\n        agent[\"model\"] = {\n            \"primary\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n            \"fallbacks\": [\n                \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5\",\n                \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed\"\n            ]\n        }\n        print(f\"Updated coding-agent: {old} -> {agent['model']}\")\n\nconfig_path.write_text(json.dumps(config, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\nprint(\"Written:\", config_path)\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108894,"output":400,"cacheRead":25986,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135280,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775183668174,"responseId":"061e5a34375