{"type":"message","id":"f4d8c633","parentId":"ec598c32","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:57:37.084Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me give the user a concise summary.","thinkingSignature":"4cb62d292e829085c40620e2d358394073c695b7a31b16009fd74685bdd91414"},{"type":"text","text":"已继续并落地。本轮验收件：\n\n**新 cron 已配置**\n- 脚本：`scripts/cron_conservative_shadow.sh`\n- 执行时间：每个交易日下午 16:00\n- 逻辑：跑 `run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py --profile conservative` 并写日志\n- 提交：`9d65476da`\n\n**当前状态快照**\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|---|---|\n| governance gate | **PASS** ✓ |\n| 市场风险模式 | `halt`（risk_off=true, hard_stop=true）|\n| 交易状态 | `BUY_HALT` |\n| 防御盘（defensive）| GREEN，净值 99.12万 |\n| 其他 7 个 profile | YELLOW（stale_file 为主因，非真实风险）|\n\n**说明**：市场当前仍在 `FULL_HALT`，conservative shadow 方向已确认成立，但系统不推进开仓。等市场恢复到 `cautious` 以上才有可能触发新的 shadow 信号。每日 cron 会持续跟踪。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119715,"output":230,"cacheRead":25986,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775185047943,"responseId":"061e5f985f249adea95ee9023beaa895"}}
