{"type":"message","id":"d7f6d224","parentId":"4762fb01","timestamp":"2026-04-03T03:38:17.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is very clear from the logs. Both `coding-agent` and `xiaoguanjia` are failing because:\n\n1. They're trying to use `gmn/gpt-5.4` (the OLD model that was configured before the change)\n2. They get a 503 error: \"当前账号池负载较高或模型名称配置错误，系统正在全力修复中\" (the account pool load is too high or the model name configuration is wrong)\n3. The fallback chain is: gmn/gpt-5.4 → codex/gpt-5.4 → minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\n\n\n4. The fallback chain fails and never successfully calls MiniMax\n\nBut wait, I'm confused about the timing here. We switched both agents to use MiniMax-M2.7 as primary just before 10:54, yet they're still trying to use the old gmn/gpt-5.4 model in the 11:30 logs. I think the issue is that OpenClaw cached the configuration when it started, and the running gateway process needs to be restarted to pick up the new model assignments.\n\nLooking at the error logs more carefully, the `xiaoguanjia` agent is the one that's actually failing with 503s and timing out. It's configured with gmn/gpt-5.4 as primary and falls back to codex/gpt-5.4, but both are failing—the gmn endpoint returns a 503 error about account pool load being too high or incorrect model configuration, while the codex fallback also appears to be hitting issues.\n\nThe real problem is that the fallback chain isn't working as expected. Even though I updated the config file to use MiniMax-M2.7 as the primary, the running gateway process is still using the old config from when it started, so it's never actually attempting to use the MiniMax fallback that would work.\n\nI need to restart the gateway so it picks up the new configuration and can successfully route to MiniMax. Looking at the logs, it seems both xiaoguanjia and coding-agent might actually be responding fine through the main session—the real problem is that they haven't fallen back to MiniMax yet because the old config is still cached in the gateway process.","thinkingSignature":"135796595da050618a237773825d1390702b8105ab5c57c96185b3f33c2f5e7f"},{"type":"text","text":"根因找到了。两个 bot 都在尝试用 `gmn/gpt-5.4`，但 gmn 接口持续返回 503（负载高/配置错误），fallback 链没走到 MiniMax。Gateway 重启后才能加载新配置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qu50ihxcsz6i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart 2>&1; sleep 5; openclaw gateway status 2>&1 | grep -E \"Runtime|Service|state|PID\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":121773,"output":597,"cacheRead":25986,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775187467198,"responseId":"061e690b295a6d230c997973e6d065c8"}}
