{"type":"message","id":"58a1dae0","parentId":"dd5a9fe7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:22:24.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what model I am. This is the main session, which according to the config uses `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7` as primary.","thinkingSignature":"f2800713a203c3d4aff17ba4ba2d7195bfbbfa41e71680f806d225b7cea907e1"},{"type":"text","text":"我是 **MiniMax-M2.7**（当前主会话）。\n\n你的 openclaw 配置里各机器人的模型如下：\n\n| 机器人 | 当前模型 |\n|---|---|\n| 主脑（来福来财） | `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7` |\n| 周到（小管家/xiaoguanjia） | `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7` ✅（刚已切换）|\n| Coding Agent | `minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7` ✅（刚已切换）|\n\n之前不回复的原因是 `gmn/gpt-5.4` 接口持续 503，fallback 链没来得及切换到 MiniMax。Gateway 重启后应该就好了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":150830,"totalTokens":151097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775193731562,"responseId":"061e8184adb54ea5b9037a181320c332"}}
